INSERT INTO `horoscope_content` VALUES (1,'2023-01-02',8,'horoscope','An atmosphere of serenity will prevail at home today and tensions will take a back seat. So gather with your dear ones and spread the joy. You have to find new ways of dealing with the frustration in life, which seems to get mounted gradually due to various reasons. Your insight will help you to find a way out.'),(2,'2023-01-02',7,'horoscope','A buzz and excitement will fill your home today, dear Scorpio, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss. If you\'re observing the holiday with your family, be sure to add some flare to the mix, honoring your traditions while adding a fresh spin. Don\'t be afraid to access your sentimental side later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, helping you deepen the bonds with your loved ones. Try not to stay up past your bedtime, or a square between the moon and Uranus could trigger moodiness.'),(3,'2023-01-02',10,'horoscope','Your popularity will benefit from a cosmic boost this morning, dear Scorpio, thanks to a sweet exchange between the sun and moon. Lean into these supportive vibes by using your voice, as your charisma and wit can help you win the favor of others. However, you\'ll need to slow down later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars, making it a good time to lay low. The nodes of fate will be active this evening, asking you to think creatively about the future. Meanwhile, Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, encouraging you to believe in your dreams. '),(4,'2023-01-03',8,'horoscope','A buzz and excitement will fill your home today, dear Scorpio, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss. If you\'re observing the holiday with your family, be sure to add some flare to the mix, honoring your traditions while adding a fresh spin. Don\'t be afraid to access your sentimental side later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, helping you deepen the bonds with your loved ones. Try not to stay up past your bedtime, or a square between the moon and Uranus could trigger moodiness.'),(5,'2023-01-04',8,'horoscope','You may become burnt out with the daily grind today, dear Scorpio, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. Feelings of boredom and elevated stress levels will accentuate these sentiments, though catering to your health and sense of wellness can help pull you through your to-do list. Luckily, you\'ll feel in control of your emotions as the Aquarius moon cozies up to Saturn, helping you find the endurance to persevere. Good vibes will flow as the day comes to a close and Luna enters Pisces, encouraging you to access your imagination throughout the next two days. '),(6,'2023-01-02',8,'love','Your popularity will benefit from a cosmic boost this morning, dear Scorpio, thanks to a sweet exchange between the sun and moon. Lean into these supportive vibes by using your voice, as your charisma and wit can help you win the favor of others. However, you\'ll need to slow down later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars, making it a good time to lay low. The nodes of fate will be active this evening, asking you to think creatively about the future. Meanwhile, Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, encouraging you to believe in your dreams. '),(7,'2023-01-01',8,'horoscope','Don\'t be afraid to embrace your wild side, dear Scorpio, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs ego, drama, and fun. These vibes are perfect for getting imaginative with your image, especially when Luna cozies up to Neptune this afternoon. A passionate and romantic energy will find you later in the afternoon when the moon blows a kiss to Venus, so be sure to invest some TLC into that special someone. Your thoughts will be profound as the day comes to a close, and Pluto is activated by the moon. '),(8,'2022-12-31',8,'horoscope','You\'ll feel as though you can take on the world today, dear Scorpio, as the Aries moon and Jupiter collide in your solar sixth house. These vibes are perfect for chipping away at your goals, as the effort you showcase today will have positive and lasting impacts tomorrow. Feel free to speak honestly and from a place of love as the hours continue to pass, while Mercury and Venus align in the sky. Take a moment to meditate on any people or situations who might be holding you back as Luna blows a kiss to Mars later in the afternoon. '),(9,'2022-12-30',8,'horoscope','The moon continues its journey through fiery Aries and your solar sixth house today, dear Scorpio, helping you wrap up your professional to-do list before the weekend kicks off. Just remember to nurture your body with healthy foods and plenty of water, or you could end up hitting a wall. The stars will ask you to bring order to your home this evening when Luna blows a kiss to responsible Saturn. Watch out for mental chatter or miscommunications later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury, thickening the air with a tension that could result in arguments and personal anxiety. '),(10,'2022-12-29',8,'horoscope','The vibe will be light, sweet, and harmonious today, dear Scorpio, as the moon migrates into sensual Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs love. Use this energy as an excuse to unapologetically pamper yourself, as the universes will support your mission for relaxation and luxury. If you\'re in a relationship, consider bringing your sweetie along for the ride, nurturing your relationship with yummy foods or perhaps a couple\'s massage. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sky, allowing you to seriously discuss what\'s in your heart, and what the future of your romantic entanglements might look like in the new year.'),(11,'2022-12-28',8,'horoscope','The spirit of the season will fill your soul today, dear Gemini, as the moon moves through Aquarius and the spiritual sector of your chart. Your high vibes will help elevate others, so be sure to spread some joy to your family and friends. You\'ll feel inspired to help dreams come true later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars. However, try not to overwhelm yourself trying to meet the expectations of others. Give yourself permission to retreat into your cocoon as the evening comes to a close and the moon squares off with Uranus, putting you in the mood for solitude. '),(12,'2022-12-27',8,'horoscope','You may feel as though too many people need your assistance and attention today, dear Gemini, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. Meanwhile, the Aquarius moon will leave you inspired to help others, though a cosmic alliance between Luna and Saturn will remind you to prioritize your needs first. These vibes are all about exercising healthy boundaries, so don\'t feel guilty about drawing lines where they\'re needed. You\'ll notice a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon migrates into Pisces, elevating your intuition throughout the next two days, especially where professional matters are concerned. '),(13,'2023-01-02',8,'career','You may not be in the most social mood today, dear Gemini, as the moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs privacy. With the new year only hours away, these vibes will ask you to reflect on the last twelve months while looking for ways to improve as 2023 rolls in. The beauty of this luminary placement is that it will support your desire to break away from patterns you need to outgrow, helping you implement healthier habits and build better relationships in the year ahead. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sector of your chart that governs transformation, cosmically supporting your mission for change. '),(14,'2022-12-21',1,'horoscope','Although you’re poised to party, there’s still a lot to do so you can finish 2022 strong. You may get a sudden second wind today for your work today as the energizing Sun blasts into industrious Capricorn and your ambition arena for the next four weeks. A hybrid holiday may have to be the answer because career inspiration is bound to strike at the most unexpected moments between now and January 20. Slip off as needed—but try not to leave the celebrations for TOO long.\n'),(15,'2022-12-21',1,'horoscope','A sparkling and supportive energy will find you when Jupiter, the planet of luck and growth, enters your sign. This planetary placement is poised to turn the wheels of fortune in your favor, so be sure to pursue your goals enthusiastically. Meanwhile, the Scorpio moon squares off with Saturn, highlighting how your social life has become too distracting. Luckily, the vibe will lighten just before afternoon settles in, bringing forth inspiration when Luna blows a kiss to dreamy Neptune. You\'ll feel a shift as the witching hour nears and the moon enters Sagittarius, activating the spiritual sector of your chart. \n'),(16,'2022-12-21',1,'horoscope','You may feel a bit tied down today. It won\'t necessarily be a bad day, but you may wonder about certain aspects of your family life. Don\'t try and kid yourself. You should think hard about what you want for your family for the next few years and how you intend to go about getting it.\n'),(17,'2022-12-22',1,'horoscope','Abundance isn’t just a word on divination decks and angel cards, Aries! It’s a vital mindset to embrace if you’re going to bust through a limiting plateau and reach your loftiest goals! Today, as dazzling Venus lights up your house of career success and fist-bumps alchemical Uranus in your money house, your manifestation mojo is spiking. Focus on something you REALLY want to attract to you, visualize it completely, then act as if it’s already happened. Then sit back and wait!'),(18,'2022-12-22',1,'horoscope','Your day will be filled with surprises, dear Aries, as Venus shares a sweet exchange with unpredictable Uranus. Keep your eyes peeled for new opportunities and small moments of beauty, as the universe seeks to enrich your life. Chance encounters could manifest by mid-morning when the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, making it a good time to flex your social muscles. Try to stay grounded this afternoon when Luna aligns with Neptune, or your psyche may slip away into a world of daydreams. You\'ll feel a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Capricorn, asking you to implement healthy boundaries.  '),(19,'2022-12-22',1,'horoscope','Your transmission may be stuck in reverse today, Aries. This doesn\'t mean you can\'t be productive. You may need to change your approach. Carefully assess a situation before you proceed. Someone may be trying to cross you. Be smart about your rebuttal. Head-on combat isn\'t the best approach. Try reasoning. You may discover that there are pieces of the puzzle you didn\'t know about.'),(20,'2022-12-23',1,'horoscope','Your meteoric ascent can’t wait until 2023, Ram! Today’s skies feature the year’s second new moon in Capricorn and your tenth house of career success, and because this one is also a supermoon, it can accelerate your biggest dreams. Your spontaneous sign likes to enter a situation at full strength, but this requires you to be strategic instead. Over the coming two weeks, focus on your intentions and wishes, actually envisioning how life will look and feel when you’re there. Then do something bold and audacious to broadcast the message that you\'re raring to go. '),(21,'2022-12-23',1,'horoscope','The Capricorn new moon manifests early this morning, dear Aries, asking you to set intentions around your career goals for the year ahead. Work with these vibes by visualizing where you hope to be six months from now, including as much detail as you can muster. Try not to make any commitments you\'re not sold on this evening when Luna forms an unbalanced aspect with Mars, or you could end up breaking your word. Consider paying down any debts you owe this evening when the moon connects with the nodes of fate, asking you to invest in your financial health. '),(22,'2022-12-23',1,'horoscope','Your meteoric ascent can’t wait until 2023, Ram! Today’s skies feature the year’s second new moon in Capricorn and your tenth house of career success, and because this one is also a supermoon, it can accelerate your biggest dreams. Your spontaneous sign likes to enter a situation at full strength, but this requires you to be strategic instead. Over the coming two weeks, focus on your intentions and wishes, actually envisioning how life will look and feel when you’re there. Then do something bold and audacious to broadcast the message that you\'re raring to go. '),(23,'2022-12-24',1,'horoscope','Don\'t be afraid to share your most inspired ideas today, dear Aries, as chatty Mercury blows a kiss to dreamy Neptune. These vibes can help you get ahead within your professional ambitions, though you\'ll want to perfect your visions before showcasing them to the world. Your intuition will benefit from a boost when the Capricorn moon joins in, helping you read your colleagues and superiors on an intimate level. Be sure to recite a few positive mantras while reinvesting in a belief in self this evening, when Luna crosses over empowering Pluto before migrating into Aquarius and your solar eleventh house. '),(24,'2022-12-24',1,'horoscope',' You\'ve been more thoughtful lately and truer to yourself. This is due to your recent introspection. You really can change your life. All it takes is time and commitment. You\'ve made great progress in your development. Continue on this path and you will wind up in a much better place. Keep your eye on the goal, but don\'t be so focused that you forget to enjoy the journey.'),(25,'2022-12-24',1,'horoscope','You are confused by the mixed signals from a colleague. Keep your thoughts to yourself. Try not to argue about trivial matters. A new avenue is opening up at work which will provide the base for much pleasure in the future. Children or loved ones may be landing much heavier responsibilities on you than usual. Lucky Colour: Copper. Lucky Number: 5.'),(26,'2022-12-25',1,'horoscope','The moon moves through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs community, dear Aries, putting you in the mood for companionship and fun. Use this energy as an excuse to spread tidings and cheer to your extended friendship circle, showing the people in your life that you care. You\'ll feel motivated to put action behind your words and ideas later in the afternoon, thanks to a sweet exchange between Luna and Mars. Try not to let a stubborn demeanor ruin your fun as the day comes to a close and Luna squares off with Uranus, threatening to trigger tension. '),(27,'2022-12-25',1,'horoscope','You may not want to wander far from your bedroom today. That\'s fine. Take this opportunity to get things done around the house that make you feel like your energy is an important part of the atmosphere. Hang new pictures, read inspiring articles, and laugh at magazine cartoons that inspire your humorous side. Be soft and gentle with your words and actions. Just take it easy!'),(28,'2022-12-25',1,'horoscope','You will earn well. Your efforts will pay off in this direction. You will witness growth in your business. You will also enjoy stability in your job. You will be able to finish your work in time. This will give you lot of respect and fame. You will also have expansion plans in your business and you will work in partnership. Time will be favorable for you. There will be sweetness in marital relations. You will be very busy with your home affairs too. Don\'t tell your business secrets to any person. Students will perform well. You will also get admission in institutes of your own choice. Husband and wife will share wonderful bonding. Marriage of a family member will get fixed all of a sudden.\n\n'),(29,'2022-12-26',1,'horoscope','You may find it difficult to move forward from the past, dear Aries, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. Try not to let gloomy memories weigh you down, or you could begin to feel out of touch with yourself. Luckily, you\'ll find stability and strength within your community when the Aquarius moon cozies up to Saturn early this morning. Give yourself permission to hide away from the world as the day comes to a close and Luna migrates into Pisces. encouraging you to fly under the radar to soothe your mind, body, and soul'),(30,'2022-12-26',1,'horoscope','Don\'t expect a reaction from people today even if you tell the funniest jokes. Others are likely to be reserved and uptight. For the most part, the day\'s forecast calls for conservative skies and a slight chance of grumpiness. The best way to handle this is to engage in activities that require discipline, grounding, and efficiency. Finish your chores and plan fun things for evening.'),(31,'2022-12-26',1,'horoscope','You’re picky about who you let close to you Aries, but once you find the right click, you love being a part of a solid group. But today, as the moon collides with structured Saturn, you may realize that a close friendship could benefit from stronger boundaries. It feels awkward to have to tell someone, for instance, that you’re not comfortable with their gossiping about a mutual friend or making mean-girl jokes about a colleague. But if you don’t, chances are they’ll never stop on their own.'),(32,'2022-12-27',1,'horoscope','A soft energy will lift your spirits this morning, dear Aries, as the Pisces moon blows a kiss to the sun. Bring these good vibes to work, and approach the day with an optimistic and compassionate disposition. Unfortunately, you may begin to feel a touch temperamental later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars. Luckily, a helping hand from the nodes of fate will allow you to reconnect with your sense of gratitude this evening, so be sure to stop and smell the roses. Meanwhile, Venus shares a sweet exchange with Neptune, helping you manifest your dreams into reality. '),(33,'2022-12-27',1,'horoscope',' If at first you don\'t succeed, try, try again. This is your maxim for the day, Aries. What have you done lately to improve the way you live your life? Would you consider taking off on some wild adventure without looking back? Today you may meet some people who will make you want to. They\'re adventurers looking for thrills and chills, with all the risks that come along with them.'),(34,'2022-12-27',1,'horoscope','Dramatic conversations can wait, and those non-urgent texts can, too. You\'ve got way better things to do today than put out fires for other people, Aries—especially since you didn’t start them in the first place! With the moon lounging in Pisces and your twelfth house of rest, relaxation and fantasy, you\'ll be happier doing less than you will be trying to cram in more. Keep your plans flexible and remain spontaneous. Something magical could open up that turns the tide in the best possible direction. '),(35,'2022-12-28',1,'horoscope','You\'ll feel quiet yet content today, dear Aries, as the moon continues its journey through dreamy Pisces and your solar twelfth house.  A creative energy will wash over you when Luna cozies up to Neptune this afternoon, though you could find yourself lost in a daydream if you don\'t funnel these visionary vibes productively. A sweet exchange between the moon and Venus will help you feel supported within your professional goals, but don\'t be afraid to ask for additional advice or assistance if you need it. You may want to keep a pen and paper handy when you crawl under the covers tonight as Pluto and the moon conspire to bring you meaningful dreams. '),(36,'2022-12-28',1,'horoscope','Today you may be overcome by a current of humanist thought, Aries. Your consciousness is traveling, and you probably couldn\'t care less about the details of the events going on around you. You\'re freethinking, which is inspired by your spirit of fairness. You may even be in a situation where you have to act as a kind of \"enlightened\"\" referee'),(37,'2022-12-28',1,'horoscope','Letting go of how you think things SHOULD go is never easy for your in-control sign, but trust us, surrender is the key to peace of mind! You may think that grasping tighter gives you power over the circumstances, but actually it just perpetuates their toxic influence on your life. The sooner you loosen your grip, the quicker you’ll be able to recover all that wasted energy. Chances are, your fears are far more inflated than the reality of the situation.'),(38,'2022-12-29',1,'horoscope','Today will be a lucky day for you, sweet Ram, as the moon creeps into your sign and crosses over auspicious Jupiter this morning. You may awaken to good news, fresh opportunities, or a sense that possibility lies around each corner, thanks to these supportive vibes. Watch out for professional tension as evening rolls in and the sun and moon square off, which could create waves within your industry. Luckily, you\'ll have a chance to focus on happier topics and personal passions later tonight, thanks to a sweet exchange between Luna and Mars, bringing fire to your heart and mind. '),(39,'2022-12-29',1,'horoscope','You may surprise the people around you over the next few days, Aries. You\'re a responsible person and others can count on you. But just like anybody else, you\'re sensitive to your desires. You should expect your desires to be so strong today that they may be irresistible. If this is a positive experience, you may need to do some planning in your personal life.'),(40,'2022-12-29',1,'horoscope','Those lofty resolutions you started crafting earlier this week hit an untimely speed bump today as messenger Mercury spins retrograde in Capricorn and your ambitious tenth house. Since the best-laid plans could go awry during this three-week circuit, hold off on making any ginormous moves until Mercury pivots forward again on January 18. But we’re not saying to slam on the brakes either! This retrograde is ideal for researching everything from best-priced goods to the background files of people you want to pitch (and impress!) professionally.'),(41,'2022-12-30',1,'horoscope','Embrace all of your favorite things today, dear Aries, as the moon continues its journey through your sign. These vibes are all about putting yourself first, especially if you\'ve been going the extra mile in your professional and personal life. Try to get some socializing in this evening when Luna aligns with Saturn. Unfortunately, the vibe will get a bit rough later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury, threatening to trigger miscommunications and crossed boundaries. Tensions will continue to grow as the day comes to a close, and you may have difficulty sleeping while Luna forms tense aspects throughout the witching hours. '),(42,'2022-12-30',1,'horoscope',' There\'s an overwhelming intensity about the day that might make it difficult for you to maintain the peace, Aries. Strong opinions and courageous emotions are clashing in a climactic fashion. You might find yourself in the middle of conflicting forces if you aren\'t careful. Make sure you take care of yourself and your needs before you try to patch up things for everybody else.'),(43,'2022-12-30',1,'horoscope','Squeeze in a little \"me time\"\" today while the moon lingers in Aries. This weekend'),(44,'2022-12-31',1,'horoscope','The moon moves into sensual Taurus today, dear Aries, giving you permission to slow down, indulge in fine foods, and perhaps a bit of retail therapy. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sector of your chart that governs career, reminding you that it\'s okay to exercise spending power, especially if you\'ve been working overtime lately. This celestial alliance will also ask you to check in with your professional ambitions, especially if you\'re unhappy with your current position. These vibes are all about seeking change if you want it, so it might be a good time to refresh your resume so you can search for new opportunities in the new year. '),(45,'2022-12-31',1,'horoscope','A new energy will now begin to work in your life. You will suddenly find that balancing family and career issues have now become extremely easy. All your hesitations will disappear and your actions are marked by an unprecedented level of confidence. You will also be able to resolve any ambivalent feeling towards those near to you both in workplace and in the family.'),(46,'2022-12-31',1,'horoscope','If you are in the mood to be alone, go ahead and indulge. No need for friends and no need for music.\n\nRush to the outskirts and mingle with nature. If you deal with money matters.\n\nThere may be some money coming your way.'),(47,'2022-12-21',2,'horoscope','Have you already solidified your holiday plans? If not, you might get a wild hare to celebrate someplace very off-the-beaten-path! Today, the Sun swings into Capricorn and your ninth house of travel and adventure for four weeks. Not fully committed to a gathering of friends or family—and need to use some vacation time? Check last-minute airfare and Airbnb deals in places you’re dreaming of. And even if that trip doesn’t happen now, at least you’ll have whet your globe-trotting appetite!'),(48,'2022-12-21',2,'horoscope','The sun migrates into Capricorn and your solar ninth house today, dear Taurus, ushering in the dawn of winter and the most spiritually significant time of year for you. You\'ll feel more connected with the other side in the coming weeks. So, be sure to reconnect with your favored meditation, divination, prayer, or magickal practices. A celestial exchange between the sun and Jupiter suggests that answers can be found from within right now, so be sure to listen to your intuition. Consider taking a cleansing salt bath later this evening when the Sagittarius moon connects with Chiron and Mars.'),(49,'2022-12-21',2,'horoscope','You will find that your emotions are much more under control today, Taurus. You\'re able to strike a happy balance and avoid extraordinary extremes that scare others away. In fact, quite the opposite is true. People will be attracted to you as you provide a life raft on turbulent waters. Your sensitivity is strong and you\'re able to immediately fix on the status of any situation.'),(50,'2022-12-22',2,'horoscope','Limits…what are those? Today, you’re free to stretch well past your normal comfort zone and accomplish something you’ve been told isn’t possible. Your practical sign sometimes needs an extra reminder that if you can imagine it, you can manifest it! And under today’s electrifying trine between your ruler, creative Venus, in your visionary house and wizardly Uranus, pour all your energy into bringing this thing to life. When you believe something is possible, it’s almost easy. Give it a try!'),(51,'2022-12-22',2,'horoscope','The universe will bend over backward to support you today, dear Bull, as Venus shares a sweet exchange with revolutionary Uranus. These vibes are perfect for jump starting your goals, making it a good time to express your desires to the other side while getting to work on your agenda. You\'ll have a chance to advocate for yourself within business negotiations when the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, asking you to take control of your career path. You\'ll notice a shift later tonight when the moon migrates into Capricorn, heightening your intuition throughout the next two days. '),(52,'2022-12-22',2,'horoscope','Things should go well for you today, Taurus. There\'s an added serenity in the air that will help calm your nerves. There\'s no need to make things more complicated than necessary. The answers to things are actually quite simple. Everything you want is probably right at your fingertips. You don\'t need to go far to find what you seek.'),(53,'2022-12-23',2,'horoscope','Left to your own devices, Bull, you can be a world-class homebody who loves your creature comforts. But when wanderlust strikes, it hits you hard. And thanks to today’s new supermoon in your globetrotting ninth house, you might catch a serious case of cabin fever that all the Travel Channel shows in the world can’t cure. If you can get away in the next two weeks, you’ll have the best chance of successfully scratching that itch. But if you can’t hit the open road (or skies), do something that’ll keep you inspired, like signing up for a language or cooking class that starts right after the new year. '),(54,'2022-12-23',2,'horoscope','Be sure to honor your spirit team when you awaken this morning, dear Taurus, as the Capricorn new moon activates your solar ninth house. These vibes are all about thanking the universe for the many blessings it has bestowed upon you, while also looking for ways to build upon your circumstances. Wishes are more likely to come true during this luminary, as the other side will be eager to answer your prayers. Keep your eyes peeled for signs and synchronicities as the day comes to a close, when Luna shares a sweet exchange with revolutionary Uranus, shaking up the vibe. '),(55,'2022-12-23',2,'horoscope','Left to your own devices, Bull, you can be a world-class homebody who loves your creature comforts. But when wanderlust strikes, it hits you hard. And thanks to today’s new supermoon in your globetrotting ninth house, you might catch a serious case of cabin fever that all the Travel Channel shows in the world can’t cure. If you can get away in the next two weeks, you’ll have the best chance of successfully scratching that itch. But if you can’t hit the open road (or skies), do something that’ll keep you inspired, like signing up for a language or cooking class that starts right after the new year. '),(56,'2022-12-24',2,'horoscope','You\'re feeling confident and more comfortable in your own skin than you have in a long time, Taurus. You\'re so accomplished, why are you the last one to acknowledge it? Try to look up from your desk long enough to socialize with friends and loved ones. You\'ve been so focused on work that your relationships may have suffered a bit. Spend some quality time with those you care about, if possible.'),(57,'2022-12-24',2,'horoscope','The universe will bring love to your path today, dear Taurus, as the Capricorn moon cozies up to sweet Venus. This cosmic climate is perfect for reigniting the spark in your relationship, without causing you to put pressure on the dynamic. Good vibes will continue to flow as Mercury blows a kiss to Neptune, allowing you to connect with kindred spirits. Lean into your community for support if you need it, and be sure to share what\'s in your heart. You\'ll notice a shift as the day comes to a close as the moon enters Aquarius, putting you in a career-oriented headspace. '),(58,'2022-12-24',2,'horoscope','With your ruling planet not in a favourable position, communication could slow down. It is important to communicate with a loved one. Stand your ground but don\\\'t lose your cool today and tomorrow. Start a health regime today, as you have been highly stressed and overworked. Lucky Colour: Mustard. Lucky Number: 2'),(59,'2022-12-25',2,'horoscope','You may be in charge of maintaining order within your social sphere today, dear Taurus, as the Aquarius moon migrates through your solar tenth house. Don\'t be afraid to take control if the day starts to feel disorganized, delegating tasks to idle hands when you\'re in need of help. Luckily, you\'ll have a chance to enjoy the rewards of your hard work later in the afternoon, when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, encouraging you to embrace luxury. You may feel yourself closing off as evening comes to a close and the moon squares off with Uranus, especially if your day was full of activity. '),(60,'2022-12-25',2,'horoscope',' Things are on the upswing for you today, Taurus. People are finally coming around to see things from your perspective. There\'s no need to doubt yourself. Look in the mirror and know that the person you see is capable of accomplishing anything. Your powerful emotions are your allies. Don\'t be afraid to let your heart speak up loudly and clearly, the way it wants to.'),(61,'2022-12-25',2,'horoscope','You will have money gains. You will also be kept busy in your work and it will be a bit difficult for you to give time to your family. But still you will try to take out time for yourself and be with your family. This will boost your self confidence and also make you very happy. You will be able to complete your work all will be on target. Your bosses will praise you to the sky. Some persons may be jealous of you as a result. Concentrate just on your goals. You will reach your destination. You will have such confidence in your own abilities that you will finish your work much ahead of others. You will have no shortage of money. and will buy expensive items for your family.\n\n'),(62,'2022-12-26',2,'horoscope','Your love life could act as a distraction today, dear Taurus, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. These vibes have the potential to get in your head, and you may feel tempted to hide away from your romantic entanglements. Don\'t feel guilty if you need time for yourself, but try not to act sketchy with your significant other, and try to be honest about why you\'re taking a step back. Luckily, being present at work can help pull you out of this funk, thanks to a cosmic alliance between Luna and Saturn. You\'ll feel more social late tonight when the moon enters Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs community.'),(63,'2022-12-26',2,'horoscope','You will keep a level head today, Taurus, so take this opportunity to make rational decisions about the most intense issues on the table. Stay grounded and concentrate on what you need to do. Don\'t get caught up in the usual emotional drama. Restriction and limitation are main themes of the day that will help you reach your goals.'),(64,'2022-12-26',2,'horoscope','Although you’re naturally ambitious, your modest sign gets uncomfortable at even a whiff of self-aggrandizement. But today, as the intuitive moon fist-bumps long-range-planner Saturn in your career zone, you might be tapped for a new position that brings more money, responsibility—and prestige! Don’t shuck off the praise and attention, Taurus. You’ve been working hard for this, and good on you for finally snagging the gold ring! But no resting on your laurels. Now’s the time to think about what’s next'),(65,'2022-12-27',2,'horoscope','You may encounter a kindred spirit this morning, dear Taurus, as the sun and moon share a sweet exchange. These vibes will also encourage you to nurture your soul through community, so be sure to spread some joy in your social sphere. Watch out for tension when Luna squares off with Mars later in the afternoon, which could cause you to butt heads with others. Good vibes will flow this evening, thanks to the nodes of fate. The relationships you nurture now will likely stand the test of time, so try not to invest in anyone who brings you down. Meanwhile, Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, bringing a sweet energy to the table. '),(66,'2022-12-27',2,'horoscope','Strength of character will be your partner today, Taurus. You seem to have an aura whose intensity scares some people and attracts others. Your force of character could be the cause of some wonderful feelings and emotions for the people close to you. Don\'t try and hide your emotions. They\'re the source of your creativity.'),(67,'2022-12-27',2,'horoscope','With a Pisces moon orbiting your super-social eleventh house, the old Netflix-and-chill formula won\'t cut it for you today, Bull. While you probably aren\'t in the mood to dress up for a trip to the grocery store, an end-of-year happy hour is another story. Are you off work this week? Get some different kinds of group activities on the lineup, like cross-country skiing or a potluck dinner party. Don’t wait for others to reach out, especially if you know exactly what you’d love to get up to!'),(68,'2022-12-28',2,'horoscope','Your people-person skills may feel sharper today, dear Taurus, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and your solar eleventh house. These elevating vibes will cause your aura to have a calming and tranquil presence, and people will be drawn to your grace and healing abilities, especially when Luna codecs with Neptune and Venus this afternoon. Consider tapping into your spiritual side if you get some free time, as the universe will be eager to guide and bless you. Your intuition will be heightened when Pluto becomes active later tonight, making it a good time to dabble in the divinatory arts. '),(69,'2022-12-28',2,'horoscope',' Even if you\'re a good judge of character, Taurus, the people who know you say that you base your opinions on your personal feelings, which often affect your good judgment. Today your critics are wrong, and your judgments are as precise and objective as they can possibly be. They may even help you out of a sticky situation.'),(70,'2022-12-28',2,'horoscope','Trouble on Team Taurus? Nip this in the bud before one rogue person ruins the whole operation. With the sensitive Pisces moon in your eleventh house of collaborations, you’re tuned in to your crew. Someone might be sulking or refusing to participate. But why? It’s possible they feel hurt or slighted—for reasons real or imaginary. Before you kick them off the island, Bull, have a heart-to-heart. Letting them speak their piece might be all that’s needed.'),(71,'2022-12-29',2,'horoscope','You may experience vivid and colorful dreams early this morning, darling Bull, as the moon moves into Aries and the sector of your chart that governs the subconscious. Meanwhile, a helping hand from auspicious Jupiter will usher in good vibes and messages from beyond the veil, so be sure to document any interesting encounters you had while dancing through the astral realms. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus align in Capricorn, heightening your intuition even further. Use this cosmic climate to commune with nature and your spirituality, as the energy at play opens you up to healing, blessings, and guidance from the universe'),(72,'2022-12-29',2,'horoscope','You may have to stand by certain difficult, worrisome decisions today, Taurus. You may feel a kind of urgent need for stability in your personal life. What is really behind this feeling? Is it possible that you\'re just afraid of your desire to put everything into question in order to make a fresh start? Today you may find the answer to this question. Stay tuned.'),(73,'2022-12-29',2,'horoscope','Come sail away? Just when you were about to leave shore, circumstances may arise that force you to drop anchor and rethink your whole trajectory. Blame it on pesky Mercury, who’s made the unfortunate executive decision to turn retrograde in your worldly, adventurous ninth house today. You don’t have to cancel any exciting plans, but between now and January 18, expect itinerary adjustments, scheduling changes and other potential slowdowns with anything involving a long-distance contact. Pack an extra mobile charger!'),(74,'2022-12-30',2,'horoscope','You\'ll be deep in your own thoughts throughout the day, darling Taurus, as the moon continues its journey through Taurus and your solar twelfth house. Use this energy to sort through your psyche, but remember to show yourself plenty of compassion in the process. Pay attention to any visions that find you as evening rolls around and Luna aligns with Saturn, as your brilliant ideas could lead to career success. Your intuition will become heightened tonight as the moon squares off with Mercury. However, the messages you receive may be difficult to unpack, so try not to wrack your brain looking for answer'),(75,'2022-12-30',2,'horoscope','You may feel extra self-confident today, Taurus, making you more able to say and do the things you might normally keep inside. Be warned, however, that you\'re apt to run into some powerful, unexpected opposition. The genius in you wants to come out and show others what you\'re made of, but other people may have reason to find fault. Don\'t let others\' disapproval hinder your progress.'),(76,'2022-12-30',2,'horoscope','Long winter\'s (disco) nap, anyone? The moon drags through your sleepy twelfth house today, and it\'s all you can do to keep your eyes open. Don\'t feel bad about bailing on the pre-holiday cocktail hour or working quietly—even in solitude. This weekend\'s Taurus moon will make you feel like the belle of the ball once again. Get your rest in now so you can capitalize on that exhilarating energy. One caveat: The dancing muse could strike later tonight. If so, dress up and hit the scene for a little end-of-2022 booty-shaking.'),(77,'2022-12-31',2,'horoscope','The moon moves into your sign today, sweet Bull, elevating your mind, body, and soul just in time for your New Year\'s Eve festivities! Don\'t be surprised if you find yourself at the center of attention right now, as your aura will be blessed with charisma, allure, and glamor. Take a moment to meditate on your goals for 2023 before heading out to celebrate, as the universe will be eager to work with you. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sector of your chart that governs spirituality, empowering you and your ability to manifest your wildest dreams in the new year.'),(78,'2022-12-31',2,'horoscope','Know what astrology and the planets have in store for people born under Taurus sign. Astrology reveals the effect of planets on Taurus today.'),(79,'2022-12-31',2,'horoscope','If you are in the mood to be alone, go ahead and indulge. No need for friends and no need for music.\n\nRush to the outskirts and mingle with nature. If you deal with money matters.\n\nThere may be some money coming your way..'),(80,'2022-12-21',3,'horoscope','The reindeer you’ll be most interested in is Cupid—and is there a Vixen? Oh, wait: That’s YOU, Gemini! For the next four weeks, as the glamorous Sun struts through 