ptune, bringing forth an abundance of inspiration and empowerment from our starry sky.'),(99,'2022-12-27',3,'horoscope',' What an extraordinary day for you, Gemini! The dynamic energy in the air will help you set new personal goals. The positive feedback you get from the people around you could inspire you to make some life-changing decisions for the good of you and your family. Don\'t hesitate to share the day\'s positive attitude with them.'),(100,'2022-12-27',3,'horoscope','You might not be able to get your mind off your work, but what if you changed your outlook from “back to the grind” to something a bit more inspiring? Today, the dreamy Pisces moon is jetting through your tenth house of career ambitions, opening up your creative channels. When your mind starts to wander, don’t start thumbing through TikTok. Distraction is the enemy of innovation! Instead, try meditating or free-writing to see what’s cooking in your psyche. '),(101,'2022-12-28',3,'horoscope','Opportunities to expand your professional standing may manifest today, dear Gemini, as the moon moves through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs career. Use this energy to nurture healthy dynamics with your superiors and colleagues, showcasing your ability to relate to others and act as a team player, especially when Luna aligns with Neptune this afternoon. Invest some time and focus on your most meaningful relationships later in the day when the moon shares a sweet exchange with Venus. However, you may feel called toward solitude later tonight when mysterious Pluto becomes active in our skies. '),(102,'2022-12-28',3,'horoscope','You tend to want to explain everything that goes on around you, Gemini. You rationalize everything in an instant, and group all your experiences into great theories. But you\'ve been very quiet for quite some time now. It\'s as if something is keeping you from speaking. Today you will get a few words in, so don\'t worry.'),(103,'2022-12-28',3,'horoscope','You can deal with anything today—provided you know what the deal actually is! But it might be tricky trying to get clear on best “next steps” while today’s nebulous Pisces moon is fogging things up for everyone. You’re not going to let anything (or anyone!) get in the way of your success, so use your Spidey senses to at least try to get to the bottom of any ongoing issues. Without actually making any accusations, ask pointed questions and don’t take “I dunno” for an answer.'),(104,'2022-12-29',3,'horoscope','Your presence online will be pronounced today, dear Gemini, as the moon and Jupiter join forces in your solar eleventh house. Use this energy to stand tall on your favorite social media platforms, as doing so will allow you to find like-minded individuals and grow your following. On a personal level, you\'ll want to leave space for your heart and mind to shift directions as Mercury and Venus cross paths in the sector of your chart that governs transformation. These vibes can also help you elicit change as long as you lead from a place that\'s rooted in logic and love.'),(105,'2022-12-29',3,'horoscope',' Do you help the world evolve, Gemini? You may ask yourself this kind of delicate question today. Even if you\'re a person of action who knows how to react to situations, you should be careful not to be too impulsive. You have a specific role to play. Don\'t get thrown off track by emotional circumstances.'),(106,'2022-12-29',3,'horoscope','Feelings could get complicated quickly today, when your ruler, messenger Mercury, makes a retrograde U-turn. As the messenger planet backs up through your intimate eighth house until January 18, feelings WILL run hot and cold. Unless you’re trying to win a mirrorball trophy in the pursuer-distancer dance, don’t wait for other people’s cues before you make a move. Decide now that you’ll be proactive about keeping your most important relationships healthy…even if that means asking for a little space when you need it'),(107,'2022-12-30',3,'horoscope','You\'ll be working overtime to stay on top of your social media interactions today, dear Gemini, as the moon continues its journey through fiery Aries. Use this energy to refine your image online, especially if it\'s been a while since you updated your pages. A spiritual element will come into play as Luna blows a kiss to Saturn this evening, making it a good time to unplug and focus on meditation. The vibe could get a little intense later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury, which could lead to power struggles or arguments within your community. '),(108,'2022-12-30',3,'horoscope',' You might find that others\' strong opinions dictate today\'s actions, Gemini. The atmosphere is quite intense, so you might want to lay low and let others have their way. Don\'t try to put up a fight. Unexpected opposition may come out of nowhere and take control. There\'s a powerful force at work asking you to do things with more passion than usual.'),(109,'2022-12-30',3,'horoscope','When in doubt, pick the option that yields the best story. Imagine the thrill of calling friends with a \"You\'ll never believe what I just did…\"\" tale. Better yet'),(110,'2022-12-31',3,'horoscope','You may not be in the most social mood today, dear Gemini, as the moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs privacy. With the new year only hours away, these vibes will ask you to reflect on the last twelve months while looking for ways to improve as 2023 rolls in. The beauty of this luminary placement is that it will support your desire to break away from patterns you need to outgrow, helping you implement healthier habits and build better relationships in the year ahead. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sector of your chart that governs transformation, cosmically supporting your mission for change. '),(111,'2022-12-31',3,'horoscope','You may be provided with limited resources which will prevent you from giving a shape to your ideas. Do not get anxious as you will get a chance to do the work of your choice by the end of the day! You have inclination towards hard work and you will enjoy the freedom along with the responsibilities'),(112,'2022-12-31',3,'horoscope','If you are in the mood to be alone, go ahead and indulge. No need for friends and no need for music.\n\nRush to the outskirts and mingle with nature. If you deal with money matters.\n\nThere may be some money coming your way..'),(113,'2022-12-21',4,'horoscope','Hopefully the holidays aren’t so all-consuming that you can’t make dating and mating an equally high-priority item! Today, the radiant Sun begins its four-week trek through Capricorn and your seventh house of committed relationships. Regardless of your romantic status, this is sizzle time! If you’re single and have taken yourself out of circulation, get ready to get that life-force pumping again! Come out of your shell and give some worthy contender(s) a chance. Happily attached? Make your partner a priority and enjoy quality time together.'),(114,'2022-12-21',4,'horoscope','A harmonious and stabilizing energy will find you today, dear Cancer, as the sun enters Capricorn and the sector of your chart that governs love. This solar placement can help you feel rooted in your most valued relationships, so be sure to nurture the most important dynamics. Meanwhile, the moon continues its journey through Sagittarius, asking you to eat well, exercise, and hydrate. Try not to be overly critical of yourself or others this evening when Luna faces off with Mars, which could cause you to see the world through a more pessimistic lens. '),(115,'2022-12-21',4,'horoscope','Try not to see the negative in everything today, Cancer. Concentrate on the positive. You will pick up subtle signals from others that can be very helpful as you gather data throughout the day. As you proceed through it, keep in mind that everything need not be a race to the finish line. Enjoy where you are now. There\'s no reason to rush to the next activity if you\'re having fun.'),(116,'2022-12-22',4,'horoscope','Hard as it may be, make time for everyone today, Cancer, even if it’s just a few focused minutes. With loving Venus in your partnership sector, those connections are top priority. But because the heart-thumping planet is in a harmonious angle with communal Uranus in your house of friends and colleagues, they’re going to need a piece of you, too. The trick is to set firm time limits, and when a needy person starts to get clingy, have a kind but firm “getaway line” ready to deliver.'),(117,'2022-12-22',4,'horoscope','Do something special and unexpected for your beloved today, dear Cancer, as romantic Venus forms a sweet exchange with unpredictable Uranus. These vibes are perfect for showing that you care in unique ways as the stars push you to honor your most valued companions. Consider breaking free from unhealthy habits as the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, asking you to get serious about your health and wellness. These vibes are also perfect for getting organized, with an emphasis on throwing out unused items that have been collecting dust. You\'ll feel a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Capricorn, blessing you with a harmonious energy. '),(118,'2022-12-22',4,'horoscope','Tension may run high today as things come to a great emotional climax. It might seem as if everyone is out to get you, Cancer, but more than likely this paranoia is a figment of your imagination. Don\'t get carried away with crazy scenarios that have no basis in reality. People may be acting irrationally, so don\'t be surprised if reason and logic are nowhere to be found.'),(119,'2022-12-23',4,'horoscope','If you’re craving more than just a “mistletoe moment,” here’s why: Today’s potent new supermoon lands in Capricorn and stokes your seventh house of committed partnerships. Your relationship or status could undergo a change in the coming two weeks. If you’re searching for lasting reciprocal love, 