nutrition are luxuries you can\'t afford to ignore. You\'re burning the candle at both ends. Stop before you burn out completely!'),(123,'2022-12-24',4,'horoscope','Love will reign supreme this morning, dear Cancer, as the Capricorn moon cozies up to sweet Venus. Use this energy to prioritize your partner, but don\'t forget to show some love to yourself. Meanwhile, chatty Mercury blows a kiss to mystical Neptune, opening you up to messages from beyond the veil. Keep your eyes peeled for small moments of beauty and coincidences, as it could be the other side showcasing support. You\'ll have a chance to bury that hatchet on any conflict that may have manifested for you recently this evening, when Luna crosses over Pluto before entering revolutionary Aquarius.'),(124,'2022-12-24',4,'horoscope','A friend may turn against you so watch your words and be sure to return favours. There may be changes in business plans today. Hassles with your boss are sure to erupt if you speak your mind. Some will make a major purchase for the home. Lucky Colour: Maroon. Lucky Number: 8.'),(125,'2022-12-25',4,'horoscope','You may find yourself in an intense yet quirky mood today, dear Cancer, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and your solar eighth house. These vibes can help you form meaningful memories with your nearest and dearest, as long as you let your guard down, relax, and try to have fun. Though the pressures of the holiday season may weigh on you, don\'t be afraid to ask for a hand if you could use some help cooking goodies, setting tables, or washing dishes. Don\'t be afraid to step back and take a breather when you need to, rejoining your loved ones after you\'ve had a moment to center yourself.'),(126,'2022-12-25',4,'horoscope',' You may not feel like you\'re in tune with your situation today, Cancer. Try not to get too pushy with your opinions about how things should be done. Honor other people\'s perspectives and approaches. It may be hard for others to commit to things the same way you do. Their methods may be different, but that doesn\'t mean they are necessarily any better or worse.'),(127,'2022-12-25',4,'horoscope','The time is just right to do things in your own ways and manners. Your performance in the interviews/exams will be upto the mark and as expected of you. You will be tension free. The time is also favoring you so is your luck which is on your side. You will have new work plans for business and expansion. Your income will also rise. You will have your own days of success. You will have money in finishing your works you want to. New members will be added to the family. Auspicious functions will take pace. You will finish your work with enthusiasm, excitement and lot of hope. Your partner will support you all along\n\n'),(128,'2022-12-26',4,'horoscope','You could experience a few creative blocks today, dear Cancer, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with the healing asteroid, Chiron. Professional stress and personal responsibilities could be the culprit, making it important that you find ways to blow off steam. Luckily, a celestial alliance between the Aquarius moon and Saturn will help you find your efficiency, allowing you to cut through business easily and seamlessly. A thirst for adventure and spiritual fulfillment will come into play later tonight when Luna migrates into watery Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs philosophy, giving you a chance to reconnect with your truest self. '),(129,'2022-12-26',4,'horoscope','This is a terrific day for you, Cancer. You will feel a greater sense of appreciation and respect for the people around you. The planning and hard work you\'ve contributed recently is finally paying off. People are likely to arrive at your level of thinking. You\'ll find you can connect on a very productive level. Your emotions are under control and your thoughts crystal clear.'),(130,'2022-12-26',4,'horoscope','Don’t blink! Your unwavering attention is needed today, Cancer, as the moon syncs up with security-minded Saturn in Aquarius, activating your eighth house of joint resources. Boundary issues could get triggered. Romantically speaking, you might realize that you’re tired of always being the one to compromise. Or perhaps you sense your partner is hiding a secret. Whatever the issue, it’s worth discussing it in a calm, cool manner. That’s the first step to solving the problem, hopefully for good.'),(131,'2022-12-27',4,'horoscope','Your aura will be elevated and your heart full of love this morning, dear Cancer, as the sun and moon share a sweet exchange. Use this energy to embrace your compassionate side in an attempt to better understand the people around you. Unfortunately, you may begin to feel agitated or anxious when Luna squares off with Mars later in the afternoon, especially if you haven\'t been neglecting your spiritual side. Luckily, these vibes will also give you a chance to untangle your psyche, as long as you\'re willing to face your shadow and do a bit of emotional heavy lifting. '),(132,'2022-12-27',4,'horoscope','You can start your day without all the usual planning. Be free to discover your day as it unfolds. This might feel like it\'s against your nature, but it\'s good for you to enjoy life\'s sometimes arbitrary nature every once in a while. Otherwise, you may miss out on some of the best things life has to offer!'),(133,'2022-12-27',4,'horoscope','As much as you cherish time at Casa Crab, adventure awaits beyond your four walls. The moon is sailing through Pisces and your exploratory ninth house, beckoning you to step out and leave those domestic duties for another day. You might get a wild hare to leave work early and watch the sun set from the floor-to-ceiling window of a beautiful hotel lounge. Call someone from your friend group who’d enjoy an evening cocktail or some post-Christmas sale shopping. No matter what you get up to, a change of scenery will recharge your creative batteries. '),(134,'2022-12-28',4,'horoscope','A giddy feeling may find you today, sweet Crab, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs spirituality. Use this energy to walk a higher path, trusting that the universe has beautiful surprises in store, especially when Luna cozies up to ethereal Neptune this afternoon. Meaningful exchanges are liable to manifest later in the afternoon when the moon blows a kiss to Venus, making it a good time to show that you care, especially when it comes to love. An intimate vibe will fill the air later tonight when Pluto is activated by the moon.'),(135,'2022-12-28',4,'horoscope','As a Cancer, you don\'t really like to talk about things. Talking just isn\'t one of your specialties. Everyone has his/her own role, and yours is to take action and create, not talk about doing it. However, the planetary positions today might make you utter a few very deep words. Come on! Tell us a little something about how you feel deep inside!'),(136,'2022-12-28',4,'horoscope','Even if you’re so far OFF the same page you’re in different literary genres, try to make sense of what people are communicating today. It’s hard to “seek to understand” when you’re triggered and annoyed. But things could go from bad to dumpster fire if you don’t at least try to get down to the truth. Suck it up and initiate an honest conversation about what went wrong—or what others are currently unhappy about. You don’t have to yield, but until you know what’s what, you won’t be able to do a thing to fix it.'),(137,'2022-12-29',4,'horoscope','Your professional ambitions will be blessed with some extra cosmic support this morning, dear Cancer, as the Aries moon cozies up to auspicious Jupiter. Use this energy pursue status and success as the stars conspire to help you along this journey. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus hold hands in Capricorn, bringing a romantic energy to the air that\'s perfect for expressing your love. These vibes are also ideal for indulging in self-care, so be sure to do something that will make your heart and mind happy. Consider unplugging and spending time in solitude later this afternoon when Luna connects with Mars. '),(138,'2022-12-29',4,'horoscope','You may tend to be overprotective of the people closest to you, especially children. You may feel you live in a dangerous world in which people don\'t care about responsibility to one another. But the people you\'re trying to protect are probably better prepared and adapted to the world than you think, Cancer. They might try to tell you this even if your support is indispensable.'),(139,'2022-12-29',4,'horoscope','Are you riding on assumptions, Cancer? Mercury turns retrograde in your partnership zone today, flashing a red-hot resentment alert. You may feel “put upon” by someone who isn’t returning the same level of generosity, but we advise against entering that dark tunnel. With signals scrambling left and right between now and January 18, give your loved ones the benefit of the doubt. Equally important is NOT saying yes to requests that will leave you feeling drained or upset. Consider that people might simply be checking your availability—without expecting you to dance to their whims.'),(140,'2022-12-30',4,'horoscope','Focusing on your professional goals will bring a sense of comfort and stability today, dear Cancer, as the moon moves through Aries and the sector of your chart that governs career. Work with these supportive vibes by taking initiative around the office, as your superiors will recognize the effort you put in. Look for ways to set boundaries and receive stress when Luna connects with Saturn. Watch out for tension and miscommunications later this evening when the moon squares off with Mercury, which could be particularly problematic where matters of the heart are concerned.'),(141,'2022-12-30',4,'horoscope','Create your own reality, Cancer. It could be that you have the puppet strings in your hands, but you\'re too afraid to use them. Don\'t shy away from responsibility. Take your time and don\'t lose sight of your goals. The stakes are extra high today, and you will find that the slightest movement is magnified several times over. Be careful how you use your words. They won\'t be taken lightly'),(142,'2022-12-30',4,'horoscope','With the moon in your ambitious and unstoppable tenth house, you\'re not switching off the lights on 2022 until the job is done and dusted. Keep your nose to the grindstone, even if it’s radio silent on Slack and friends are texting you nonstop about NYE plans. Once you’ve hit your goals, log off! But first, send a strategic email announcing the completion of the project and inviting everyone to celebrate with you in spirit. In early 2023, you\'ll be the company\'s canonized superstar—and what a relief it will be to wrap this up before the celebratory weekend!'),(143,'2022-12-31',4,'horoscope','You may need to take the lead on gathering your family and friends for the new year, sweet Crab, as the moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs community. Though you can be a solitary creature at times, this luminary placement will remind you of the important role your loved ones play in nurturing your sense of emotional stability. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto cross paths in the sky, bringing a transformative energy to your love life. Work with this energy by taking steps toward the romance you desire, whether doing so involves you putting yourself out there, spoiling your sweetheart, or exercising healthier communication techniques. '),(144,'2022-12-31',4,'horoscope','You are in a fanciful mood today. Role playing and fantasies hold unusual attractions for you. You find romance everywhere and have an active fantasy life which you may get a chance to duplicate in reality. You can impulsively choose to follow an impossible dream, either in your career or your relationship. However, you should not take any major decisions now.'),(145,'2022-12-31',4,'horoscope','Will be fruitful to adopt the middle path today. Or else, you tend to take a hasty decision with your heart and not mind.\n\nThat will throw up many riddles in the future. A fruitful day for artists and creative people.\n\nAt the end of the day, you will be happy and jovial..'),(146,'2022-12-21',5,'horoscope','If you can resist everything but holiday temptations, Leo, you might need a special strategy this season. Rather than trying to (and not succeeding at) saying no thanks to things you really, really want, plan to exercise \"extreme moderation.\"\" Today'),(147,'2022-12-21',5,'horoscope','The universe will ask you to get organized within your professional ambitions throughout the next month, dear Leo, as the sun enters Capricorn and the sector of your chart that governs work. Wellness should also be a priority, so be sure to nurture your body as often as you do your career. Don\'t be afraid to call on the other side for guidance as the sun aligns with Jupiter. However, remember to stay grounded in reality when tapping into the ethereal realms. Consider unplugging from your devices this evening when the Sagittarius moon connects with Chiron and Mars, asking you to focus on what\'s real. '),(148,'2022-12-21',5,'horoscope','Try to curb your tongue today, Leo. There\'s no reason to lash out. You will find that the more sensitive your approach, the farther you will get in your pursuit of your goals. Today might find you feeling moody, and your emotions could be running away with you. Get in touch with your feelings rather than push them away. They\'re probably trying to tell you something important.'),(149,'2022-12-22',5,'horoscope','With your professional houses lit up, you may be tempted to play it a bit safe today, but don’t! Value-driven Venus is in your analytical sixth house, making the “correct” way to proceed very clear. Yet a harmonious beam from outside-the-box Uranus in your house of career success suggests that it’s actually your most imaginative ideas that will wow the decision makers. Read the room, but if you’re sensing support, unleash your most outre thoughts.'),(150,'2022-12-22',5,'horoscope','New projects or opportunities could manifest at work today, sweet Lion, as Venus and Uranus share a sweet exchange in the sky. Teamwork and helping your peers will also help you gain recognition for your efforts, which could pave the way to a promotion or higher pay. A flirty energy will permeate the air as the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, though you shouldn\'t lay all your cards on the table at once. You\'ll notice a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Capricorn, asking you to get organized in the days ahead.'),(151,'2022-12-22',5,'horoscope',' More than likely you will be caught up in a wildly intense emotional drama if you aren\'t careful, Leo. Try to stay calm and collected. Find a quiet, solitary place where you can relax. Your energy is there, but it may be more reserved and subtle on a day like this. Be the stable oasis in the raging turmoil. Make peace with the people around you.'),(152,'2022-12-23',5,'horoscope','Guilt and self-flagellation aren’t the “tools” needed to prepare for a vibrant new year, so if you’re going to treat yourself, just enjoy every morsel and sip. Then you can drop a new pin in your wellness map by thinking ahead to January as today’s new supermoon in Capricorn powers up your sixth house of healthy habits and self-care. In the sign of the goal-oriented Goat, it’ll give you support to map out resolutions and actually enjoy working out and eating more “functionally” in the next six months. Don’t overlook the SELF-nurturing part of this lunation, Leo. Holistic bodywork, stretching and soaking in salt baths can neutralize stress and keep you running like a well-oiled machine. Bring on the cacao smoothies! '),(153,'2022-12-23',5,'horoscope','You\'ll awaken with a new lease on life, dear Leo, as the Capricorn new moon manifests in your solar sixth house. These vibes are all about taking a serious approach to your goals and a sense of wellness, as the stars push you to work hard for your dreams. Though the other side will be eager to support you when it can, the responsibility to succeed will mostly lie on your shoulders. You may feel inspired to suddenly draw lines where you once were lenient later tonight when Luna shares a sweet aspect with revolutionary Uranus, encouraging self-preservation. '),(154,'2022-12-23',5,'horoscope','Guilt and self-flagellation aren’t the “tools” needed to prepare for a vibrant new year, so if you’re going to treat yourself, just enjoy every morsel and sip. Then you can drop a new pin in your wellness map by thinking ahead to January as today’s new supermoon in Capricorn powers up your sixth house of healthy habits and self-care. In the sign of the goal-oriented Goat, it’ll give you support to map out resolutions and actually enjoy working out and eating more “functionally” in the next six months. Don’t overlook the SELF-nurturing part of this lunation, Leo. Holistic bodywork, stretching and soaking in salt baths can neutralize stress and keep you running like a well-oiled machine. Bring on the cacao smoothies! '),(155,'2022-12-24',5,'horoscope','This is an auspicious time for you, Leo. It gives you the energy and enthusiasm to make the necessary changes in your life. There is a lot of work to do, but you\'re up to it! First focus on your relationships. Your loved ones don\'t care about your professional successes. They want (and perhaps need) to spend more time with you. Do what you can to bring your life more into balance.'),(156,'2022-12-24',5,'horoscope','You\'ll find yourself in a whimsical headspace without pulling the wool over your own eyes, dear Leo, as Mercury blows a kiss to ethereal Neptune. These vibes are perfect for getting organized within your most pressing agendas, though you\'ll need to accept the ups and downs of transformation in order to step into any new roles you\'re hoping to take on. Meanwhile, the moon continues its journey through Capricorn, helping you move with authenticity and charisma. You\'ll notice a shift later tonight when Luna migrates into Aquarius, bringing excitement to your love life throughout the next two days.  '),(157,'2022-12-24',5,'horoscope','You\\\'ve sorted out so much in your life recently, Have fun with friends and accept new social offers. You can’t go wrong today - everything you do may turn out fine. . Work load increases. Be tolerant, but don\\\'t let anyone take you for granted. Lucky Colour: Mango. Lucky Number: 6.'),(158,'2022-12-25',5,'horoscope','A playfulness will reside in your heart today, sweet Lion, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs love. Be generous with your joy, intellect, and compassion right now, honoring the holiday spirit while connecting with your nearest and dearest. Consider organizing a tournament or board game session later in the afternoon, when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, triggering healthy competition and unity. However, you may need to head to bed at a reasonable hour, as a square between the moon and Uranus will likely cause you to hit a wall. '),(159,'2022-12-25',5,'horoscope','Try not to be too competitive today, Leo. The more you try to drive your point across, the more it will meet stubborn opposition. This is a better day to observe the situation. Emotions are running high, and people aren\'t necessarily acting rationally. It will do no good to try to reason with someone determined to fight. Save your ammunition for something else.'),(160,'2022-12-25',5,'horoscope','It will turn out to be a wonderful week. Students will concentrate on studies and will get good results. Your business activities will speed up. You will have no tensions about your future. You will also have no shortage of funds. You will buy lot of items for your house hold needs. You will move forward in your life. You will have the blessings of your seniors/elders. You will also have the support of your loved ones. You will enjoy their company a lot. Your friends will also support you. You will make new investments. Your children will be a cause of delight for you. They will do well in their field of work. Lovemates will have a great time.\n\n'),(161,'2022-12-26',5,'horoscope','Self-love can help you feel more secure within yourself and your romantic life, dear Leo, as the Aquarius moon cozies up to stabilizing Saturn. Use this energy as an excuse to move at your own pace today, taking time to breathe deeply, appreciate your surroundings, and stretch throughout the day. These vibes are all about establishing harmony, making it important that you roll with any punches the universe throws your way. Luckily, the vibe should be fairly easygoing. However, you may need to lean into your spirituality and optimism if your emotions begin to rise. You\'ll find yourself in a private mood as the day comes to a close and Luna glides into watery Pisces. '),(162,'2022-12-26',5,'horoscope','There\'s a restrictive, sober tone to the day that may wear you down, Leo. The trick to working this energy to your advantage is to adjust your game plan to fit the mood. Take care of mundane chores and small obstacles. Make realistic plans and follow through with short-term goals. Water your plants. Do things that require discipline and grounding.'),(163,'2022-12-26',5,'horoscope','Partnerships can flip from light-and-breezy to dark-and-stormy in the time it takes to read an email. Today, the emo moon merges with playing-for-keeps Saturn in Aquarius, your realm of dynamic duos. In business and in love, you may suddenly feel the need to establish clearer boundaries and to bring up issues of accountability. Everything in good stead? This is a perfect opportunity for a relationship tune-up. Single? It might be time to up the ante by hiring a love coach or professional matchmaker.'),(164,'2022-12-27',5,'horoscope','Nurture your healthiest habits this morning, dear Leo, as the Pisces moon blows a kiss to the Capricorn sun. This celestial exchange will push you to evolve and transform, though you\'ll need to start with small yet meaningful steps. Watch out for drama within your social sphere later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars. Consider stepping away from your social media pages during this time, or you could find yourself in a heated debate. New opportunities could alter your professional path this evening, thanks to a helping hand from the nodes of fate. Meanwhile, Venus shares a sweet exchange with Neptune, helping you feel supported from beyond the veil. '),(165,'2022-12-27',5,'horoscope','In general, you tend to be critical of the way the government and politicians handle social issues and institutions. Your goal isn\'t just to criticize, however. You would also like to see some positive changes in these areas. The aura of understanding and comprehension in the air today helps you realize that if you want the world to evolve, you\'re going to have to get people to react.'),(166,'2022-12-27',5,'horoscope','Rolling in the deep is not for amateurs, but you’re ready to take the plunge today, Leo. With the Pisces moon beaming in your eighth house of mystery and seduction, you’re like a one-Lion psychic hotline. If someone seems to be withholding important intel, stop asking for details and do your own sleuthing. As you dig beneath the surface, you could discover that a mutual attraction’s been brewing. Intense! It’s not something you NEED to act on (unless, of course, you want to), but you CAN let yourself enjoy the thrill of this secret admission.'),(167,'2022-12-28',5,'horoscope','A cleansing and supportive energy will surround you today, dear Leo, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs transformation. Use this luminary placement to release that which is no longer serving you, as doing so will help you to feel empowered and in control of your situation. Luckily, transitions will come easily this afternoon when Luna cozies up to Neptune. This celestial alliance can help dissolve your cares as long as you\'re honest with yourself about what they are and whether or not they\'re worth worrying about in the first place. '),(168,'2022-12-28',5,'horoscope','Scientists seem to live in a world apart from the rest of us, Leo, and from the events in everyday life, because they\'re so absorbed in other realities. This is a lot like your universe. If you were a scientist, you might do what they sometimes do - make parallels, like those learned men who apply their scientific reasoning to events in the world by analogy. Tell us your theories!'),(169,'2022-12-28',5,'horoscope','I am Leo—hear me purr? Today\'s foxy fusion of the seductive moon in your steamy eighth house and love planet Venus lures out the jungle cat in you. Scratching your carnal itches won’t be hard, but these gentle planets require a more intimate connection to truly satisfy you. Everyone adores a beautiful face, but if this is going to go anywhere, you need to mesh on a soul level too. In a relationship? Try to get any practical stuff out of the way quickly so you can relax into a sexier groove after work.'),(170,'2022-12-29',5,'horoscope','The moon creeps into Aries and the sector of your chart that governs spirituality early this morning, dear Leo, elevating your spirit throughout the next two days. An bundance of support from beyond the veil will come into play as dawn breaks and Luna cozies up to Jupiter, marking the ideal occasion to meditate on your goals. Try to bring structure to your dreams when the sun and moon square off, or you could begin to lose focus on what\'s important. Invest some time and energy in your community later tonight, when Luna blows a kiss to fiery Mars. '),(171,'2022-12-29',5,'horoscope',' You probably need society\'s or other people\'s approval in order to feel good about yourself, Leo. But your original personality and way of thinking are often hard for others to accept. You may need to make your ideas less crazy and a little more down to Earth and practical. This should be your goal over the next few days if you don\'t want to feel left out of things.'),(172,'2022-12-29',5,'horoscope','Comparison is not just the thief of joy—it’s a senseless detour to take when you’re the zodiac’s most fabulously creative sign. Remember that! Heck, tattoo it on your forehead because today Mercury spins retrograde in your perfectionistic sixth house until January 18. Fight the urge to follow someone else’s lead instead of trusting your own knowing. If you have to step back from certain social scenes in order to get grounded, do so. Meditate, exercise, feed your body clean fuel. Ease into 2023 without placing high-pressure expectations on yourself. That’s how you’ll create a fertile garden for new possibilities in your life!'),(173,'2022-12-30',5,'horoscope','Be sure to practice good karma today, dear Leo, as the moon continues its journey through Aries and your house of spirituality. You may also feel called to seek adventure, so don\'t be afraid to step into the unknown. Allow yourself to dream big as Luna blows a kiss to Saturn this evening, bringing a supportive and creative energy to the table. However, you may want to access your practical side later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury, or your fantasies may remain as such for the foreseeable future. Try to fit in a meditation session before bed, or you may find that sleep is difficult to find.'),(174,'2022-12-30',5,'horoscope','Things that you thought were obvious may not seem quite as clear as you\'d like them to be, Leo. Be aware that there may be some intense opposition to your plans. Take care of other people and their emotions. You will find that a wall might suddenly go up, putting a harsh barrier between you and your goals. Consider your heart as well as your head.'),(175,'2022-12-30',5,'horoscope','Speaking your truth is the only way to go today, even if that means rocking the boat a bit. Authenticity may ruffle feathers, but if you\'re coming from an honest place, people won\'t be able to dispute you. Even though you\'re naturally compassionate, you can also dole out some really tough love. Just put yourself in the other person\'s shoes before you unleash a diatribe of well-meaning advice. Today, a certain someone may be too emotionally raw to receive your words in the helpful spirit in which they are intended.'),(176,'2022-12-31',5,'horoscope','Though the weekend has just begun, you\'ll be focused on your professional ambitions, dear Leo, as the moon moves into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs career. With the new year only hours away, it\'s only natural that you\'ll be thinking of ways to improve in 2023, and excelling within your field will play a major role in your personal evolution. Take a moment to outline milestones you hope to hit throughout the next twelve months, making a personal vow to meet or exceed them. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto join hands in the sector of your chart that governs work and daily routines, suggesting that you may want to implement a more consistent schedule moving forward.'),(177,'2022-12-31',5,'horoscope','Life has been full of ups and downs lately. But soon you are going to get rid of all these. Maintain your optimistic attitude like always and things will work out better. People may approach you for help and this is good, being busy will make you forget all your worries.'),(178,'2022-12-31',5,'horoscope','You will open your heart to someone special today, and spill all your hidden desires and feelings. You will say everything you feel truthfully.\n\nYour love and attention is likely to be reciprocated. It is a good day, for romance is in the air.'),(179,'2022-12-21',6,'horoscope','Hello, glamazon! Today marks the Sun’s sultry passage into Capricorn and your flirty, flamboyant fifth house, just in time for the holidays! If you already have plans to celebrate with your beloved, then kick back and enjoy the exciting crescendo to the festivities. But if you’re still deciding where and with whom to open presents and raise some glasses of good cheer, don’t limit your possibilities! If you’re single, don’t underestimate your magnetism and manifesting power during this interlude. Dress to the nines and hit the scene. Romance awaits!'),(180,'2022-12-21',6,'horoscope','You’ll feel both playful and serious in the coming weeks, dear Virgo, as the sun enters Capricorn and your solar fifth house. This solar placement will ask you to prioritize creativity and fun, though abandoning your responsibilities in the meantime would be a mistake. Meanwhile, the Sagittarius moon connects with Mars and Chiron this evening, encouraging you to lay low from the comfort of home. As you relax from the safety of your space, look for ways to shake off any work-related stress that may have been plaguing you, and don\'t be afraid to set boundaries with anyone or anything that\'s been generating frustration'),(181,'2022-12-21',6,'horoscope',' Your thinking is clear today, Virgo, and you will find that generally things are running smoothly. Your perspective on everything is very much in line with where you need to be at this time. In other words, you\'re doing everything exactly right. Be yourself and let other people adapt to your way of thinking. There\'s no need to keep hiding the truth of who you really are.'),(182,'2022-12-22',6,'horoscope','Got a big ask to make, Virgo? Don’t keep it a secret any longer! There are plenty of seen and unseen hands that are eager to support you in achieving your goals, but if you don’t let them know what you need, they can’t help you! Today, as eloquent Venus syncs up with metaphysical Uranus, put those wishes in writing: in your journal and on social media AND perhaps articulate them to appropriate people. Nervous? Think of it like this: You only stand to gain and have nothing to lose!'),(183,'2022-12-22',6,'horoscope','The universe will usher in support anytime you are authentic to yourself today, dear Virgo, as sweet Venus and revolutionary Uranus form a supportive connection. Use these vibes to tap into your playful and artistic side, looking for ways to break free from the expectations other people have set for you. You\'ll have a chance to logically sort through your feelings as the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, which could inspire you to set boundaries with overbearing or toxic people. You\'ll notice a shift later tonight when Luna migrates into Capricorn, bringing a rush of creativity your way.'),(184,'2022-12-22',6,'horoscope','You will find strength in your inner reserves today, Virgo. Don\'t hesitate to let your deepest thoughts shine through. Keep your antenna up. You will find that there\'s an electricity in the air that keeps people\'s emotions at peak level. Follow your instincts and keep in mind that this is probably your best defense against the challenges of the day. Rational thinking is'),(185,'2022-12-23',6,'horoscope','Today’s astro news is a big deal indeed: The year’s second Capricorn new moon—also a turbocharged supermoon—turns on the power in your creative, flirtatious fifth house. It’s time to step out from behind the curtain and take your place at center stage. You don’t literally have to be an artist or performer to max out on these lunar benefits (though innovators will get a special boost). Any expression of your true self and not just your work persona will have a magical aura now and for the next several months. What brainchild (or actual bambino) are you “gestating”? Get ready for your big reveal, Virgo! And definitely bump romance to the top of your priority list. Actually, you might not need to do a single thing! '),(186,'2022-12-23',6,'horoscope','The stars will be in your corner today, dear Virgo, as the Capricorn new moon manifests in your solar fifth house. These vibes are all about building yourself up, so don\'t be afraid to stroke your ego and step into the limelight. If you\'re invested in a passion project or creative endeavor, now might be a good time to showcase your work to others, as doing so can help you gain notoriety. The universe will look for ways to surprise and bless you later tonight when Luna aspects Uranus, so be sure to tap into your mystical side.'),(187,'2022-12-23',6,'horoscope','Today’s astro news is a big deal indeed: The year’s second Capricorn new moon—also a turbocharged supermoon—turns on the power in your creative, flirtatious fifth house. It’s time to step out from behind the curtain and take your place at center stage. You don’t literally have to be an artist or performer to max out on these lunar benefits (though innovators will get a special boost). Any expression of your true self and not just your work persona will have a magical aura now and for the next several months. What brainchild (or actual bambino) are you “gestating”? Get ready for your big reveal, Virgo! And definitely bump romance to the top of your priority list. Actually, you might not need to do a single thing! '),(188,'2022-12-24',6,'horoscope','You have tremendous creativity inside you, Virgo. Have you begun to use some of it? This creative cycle will last for the next month or so. Don\'t let it pass without taking advantage of it. Use the other side of your brain for a change. Take up sketching, painting, or fiction writing. What you do is less important than doing something. The simple act of creation unlocks the brain.'),(189,'2022-12-24',6,'horoscope','Love will guide you creatively this morning, dear Virgo, as the Capricorn moon crosses over sweet Venus. Use this energy to embrace your artsy side as the day kicks off, as you\'ll surely create some beautiful work. Good vibes will continue to flow as Mercury blows a kiss to ethereal Neptune, bringing a softness to your aura that\'s perfect for embracing romance. Don\'t be afraid to go deep and strengthen your bonds when Luna cozies up to Pluto this evening, encouraging you to be vulnerable. You\'ll notice a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Aquarius, shifting your focus to health and wellness'),(190,'2022-12-24',6,'horoscope','Important faces are around today who can help you make the most of current situations. An extra hour of work will bring in more money, and a hobby turns lucrative. The moon gives you a rare perception and sensitivity making you seem irresistible. Checking into a relaxation resort could give unexpected results! Lucky Colour: Butterscotch. Lucky Number: 9.'),(191,'2022-12-25',6,'horoscope','You may be called to bring organization to the day and any holiday festivities it involves, dear Virgo, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and your solar sixth house. Though you may feel responsible for making sure everyone has a good time, try not to put unrealistic expectations on yourself when it comes to nursing others. Take a moment to tidy up and get back on track later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, inspiring you to reclaim order. Unexpected blessings may find you as the day comes to a close, thanks to a connection between Luna and Uranus. '),(192,'2022-12-25',6,'horoscope',' Sink into a soft, gentle rhythm and you flow with everything around you, Virgo. Ease your mind about any worries. Your subconscious knows the way. The key today is sensitivity and intuition - your specialties. You don\'t need to be concerned about a thing. Everything will work out fine. Don\'t worry that you haven\'t prepared enough. Give yourself a break and relax.'),(193,'2022-12-25',6,'horoscope','The time will be in your favor. A problem or two here and there will not make too much difference for you. You will plan out things to your perfection. You will also finish your plans very effectively keeping in mind interests of others. Your bosses expect a lot from you and you will not disappoint anyone. You may face money problems to start with but things will be in your favor pretty soon. Students will concentrate on their studies. You will have the cooperation of your family members. Your spouse/partner will get along with you very well. After getting success in your work all your tensions and problems will be a thing of the past. You will get victory in legal battles.\n\n'),(194,'2022-12-26',6,'horoscope','Choose your words wisely today, dear Virgo, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with the healing asteroid, Chiron. Miscommunications could easily turn into power struggles under this cosmic climate, making it important that you exercise patience anytime your words are misconstrued. Meanwhile, the Aquarius moon cozies up to Saturn this morning, suggesting that it may be wise to focus on your to-do list before you indulge in any socializing either online or in the material realms. A dreamy and romantic energy will drift in just as the day comes to a close and Luna moves into Pisces. '),(195,'2022-12-26',6,'horoscope',' Come down from the clouds today, Virgo. It\'s important to connect with what\'s going on down here. It could be that you\'re missing your target because you failed to take certain details into account that are obvious to everyone else. Attend to projects that require your attention. Realistic planning and disciplined actions are the best activities to engage in.'),(196,'2022-12-26',6,'horoscope','You may still be digesting Christmas cookies, but you can start burning off those holiday indulgences now. Today, as the moon links up with disciplined Saturn in your sixth house of well-being, you may find sticking to an exercise routine or a healthy-eating plan easier than ever. Exploit this planetary lift by diving in headfirst. Join a gym—or become a regular at yours—and stream classes with a teacher that will keep you pumped up. In the work department, experiment with apps and workflow systems that can help you dial down the biggest health zapper of all…stress!'),(197,'2022-12-27',6,'horoscope','Allow your heart to guide you this morning, dear Virgo, as the sun and moon share a sweet exchange. The more open you are to love in all of its forms, the more confident, creative, and energized you will feel. Unfortunately, professional pressures could cause you to tense up later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with fiery Mars. Try to connect with your spirituality or a loved one this evening when the moon aligns with the nodes of fate. Meanwhile, Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, helping you unleash your creative potential, so be sure to channel your focus accordingly!'),(198,'2022-12-27',6,'horoscope',' Virgo, you may have felt as if something has been changing in your family environment over the last few weeks. Today you will find out what\'s been going on. Someone close to you has been going through some important changes in his or her life. You feel as if you need to be there and accompany this person on a journey of self-development.'),(199,'2022-12-27',6,'horoscope','With the soulful and sensitive Pisces moon hovering in your partnership zone, we can’t blame you for craving a greater sense of security in your relationships. But you’ll miss the mark if you approach this from an analytical Virgo perspective and start hypothesizing in your head. Since fluid Pisces is your opposite sign, you might have to abandon reason and feel your way through this. Listening intently is your secret weapon. Rather than talking about your desires, ask people how they\'re feeling. Find out what they need in order to feel comfortable taking that next step with YOU.'),(200,'2022-12-28',6,'horoscope','The stars will ask you to prioritize harmony today, dear Virgo, as the Pisces moon continues its journey through your solar seventh house. These vibes are all about leaning into love and harmony, so don\'t feel guilty about temporarily shirking your responsibilities in favor of embracing the lighter side of life, especially when Luna aligns with Neptune this afternoon. A playful energy will come to fruition later in the afternoon, creating the perfect ambiance for flirting and having fun. Your creative insights will hold some serious weight later tonight when the moon activates Pluto, so be sure to work with an artistic outlet. '),(201,'2022-12-28',6,'horoscope','You\'re often like a Zen master who doesn\'t say anything to pupils for months, until the day the pupils begin to not believe any more and find themselves growing indifferent to the whole thing. Then the master pronounces one or two phrases that are so incredibly true that no one knows what to say! You could be that Zen master today.'),(202,'2022-12-28',6,'horoscope','Has something been a little off in a key relationship, Virgo? Today’s starmap can initiate the necessary repair work. A friendly fist bump of the empathic moon and diplomatic Venus can help you cut through the emotions and defenses and get to the heart of what’s really triggering the distance you’re both feeling. Start by taking a cold hard look at your own expectations and anxieties. Later, let these loving moonbeams set a beautiful “apology tour.” Dinner on you?'),(203,'2022-12-29',6,'horoscope','You\'ll be reminded that the more you release negativity from your life, the more positivity can come in, as the Aries moon aligns with Jupiter early this morning. That\'s right, dear Virgo, the universe will give you a gentle nod that it\'s time to lay the past to rest, so you can truly evolve to the next stage of your journey. Luckily, you\'ll feel motivated and mentally prepared to embrace such shifts and prioritize your own needs, thanks to a celestial marriage between Mercury and Venus. You\'ll have a chance to break free from restrictions this evening when Luna blows a kiss to Mars. '),(204,'2022-12-29',6,'horoscope','The events of the day depend on your ability to put things into question today, Virgo. In general, you\'re good at analyzing situations when things aren\'t going well in your relationships. Now someone in your family may have a problem acting responsibly. It\'s up to that person to take care of things, but you could understand the message the person is trying to send other people with his or her behavior.'),(205,'2022-12-29',6,'horoscope','You love them, you love them not…but wait! When your cosmic custodian, Mercury, flips retrograde in your fifth house of romance and creativity today, the bloom may suddenly come off the proverbial rose. But don’t rush to stamp the situation “freshness dated.” While the first rush of novelty can never be recaptured, is there a chance to regenerate the sparks at a deeper, more intimate level? What masquerades as boredom might just be your cue to go beyond the superficial layer…yes, even with someone you THINK you know everything about. '),(206,'2022-12-30',6,'horoscope','The universe will ask you to tap into your personal power today, dear Virgo, as the moon continues its journey through fiery Aries and your solar eighth house. These vibes are perfect for boldly pursuing your goals, though you should choose your endeavors wisely and avoid trying to do too many things at once. A sweet energy will permeate the air as evening rolls in and Luna aspects Saturn, helping you bond more deeply with your significant other or bestie, so don\'t be afraid to let your guard down. Watch out for power struggles and creative blocks later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury. '),(207,'2022-12-30',6,'horoscope','Other people may tend to snap under the emotional pressure of the day, Virgo, but you\'re well suited to soar through with flying colors. You\'re ruled by your emotions and you have no problem navigating rough waters. Other people may look to you for strength and support. Trust yourself and try not to get lured off course by conflicting opinions that don\'t seem to sit right with you.'),(208,'2022-12-30',6,'horoscope','Be the eye of the hurricane today, Virgo, not the storm itself. Chaos surrounds you, but rather than getting swept into the accompanying emotions, take command. Wrangle all the moving parts into a manageable plan. Yes, this is where your leadership skills—and that bossy streak—come in handy. If it means getting the job done (instead of getting bound in endless red tape and bureaucracy) let your word be the final one. The complainers can take it up with you AFTER the holidays. Chances are, they\'ll be thanking you by then.'),(209,'2022-12-31',6,'horoscope','You\'ll be blessed in the new year, dear Virgo, as the moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs spirituality. This luminary placement is an auspicious one for you, opening the pathways toward manifesting your dreams in the year ahead. Take a few moments to connect with your higher power before the countdown to 2023 begins, communicating your gratitude and what you hope to achieve in the next twelve months. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sector of your chart that governs friendship and fun, giving you permission to dance away 2022 with your closest companions. '),(210,'2022-12-31',6,'horoscope','While the day indicates that you are going to enjoy great fun, it will be prudent to take some time in the morning and complete the tasks that you have left pending. Also, adjust and coordinate your schedule with other family members and colleagues so that no difficulties or misunderstandings arise later on. You can also get some good news today.'),(211,'2022-12-31',6,'horoscope','It is quite probable that today will be an action-packed day for you. It is going to be a progressive day for your business.\n\nLater in the day, you may retreat into your shell, and refuse company..'),(212,'2022-12-21',7,'horoscope','Snuggle up at home or hit the parties? So many options, so little time! Today, the life-giving Sun blazes into Capricorn and your fourth house of domesticity for four weeks. No doubt your heart will be pulled toward home base, but as an outgoing air sign, you’re susceptible to FOMO. What’s a decision-challenged Libra to do? Try one of your famous balancing acts, where you “curate” your invitations, make brief appearances at all of them—then scurry home to climb under that alpaca throw!'),(213,'2022-12-21',7,'horoscope','Creating a stable and steady home environment will be important to you throughout the next month, dear Libra, as the sun enters Capricorn and the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss. Use this energy to update your space and spend more time indoors as the stars push you toward the comfort of your four walls. You may also feel inspired to showcase your success through interior design choices, making it a good time to invest in any high-end goods you\'ve been fantasizing about. You\'ll find yourself in a social and flirty mood this evening when the Sagittarius moon connects with Chiron.'),(214,'2022-12-21',7,'horoscope','Listen to what other people say to you today, Libra. There are valuable experiences waiting around the corner. The important thing to do now is recognize opportunities when they arise. The road to success isn\'t always well marked. Take a chance on the road with no signs at all. You have the courage and pioneering spirit to pursue the adventurous route, so go for it.'),(215,'2022-12-22',7,'horoscope','Put your money where your mouth is! With your ruler, value-driven Venus, in your foundational fourth house, you’re crystal-clear about your beliefs and values. And under today’s biannual mashup with alchemical Uranus in your metaphysical house, you can harness the law of attraction to draw a major goal closer to you. But you need to truly believe that you can do this and—the harder part—that you actually deserve it. Need a pep talk? Call that friend who always knows exactly what to say, and be sure to listen!'),(216,'2022-12-22',7,'horoscope','You\'ll have a chance to shake off any gloom that may have been hanging over your head recently, dear Libra, as Venus shares a sweet aspect with Uranus. Don\'t feel guilty about pampering yourself right now, especially if you\'re in the midst of dealing with sorrow. You\'ll feel inspired to bring structure to your visions as the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn, so don\'t be afraid to put action behind your ideas. However, disorganization could throw you off track due to a harsh exchange between Luna and Neptune. Plan on cozying up at home as the day comes to a close and the moon moves into Capricorn. '),(217,'2022-12-22',7,'horoscope',' You may feel a bit sluggish today, Libra. Your warrior spirit would rather stay home on the couch than get up and fight. This is fine. You may simply need a break from your quest for world domination. Remember that a good leader also takes the time to sit back and reflect on recent events in order to make better plans for the future.'),(218,'2022-12-23',7,'horoscope','Kick up the heels of your bunny slippers as the year’s second Capricorn new moon lands in your domestic fourth house. (And this one is a potent supermoon.) The most powerful urge you may experience is to feather your nest, whether with a new art print or some blingy ornaments. If Chateau Libra could stand a deep clean, hire a service as a holiday gift for yourself. This galvanizing lunar lift can forebode a move for some Libras, but don’t rush into anything. These beams will be in effect for up to six months. '),(219,'2022-12-23',7,'horoscope','The Capricorn new moon manifests in the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss early this morning, darling Libra, asking you to fill your space with love. These vibes are perfect for nurturing yourself and those around you, though a tinge of nostalgia could bring a bittersweet nuance to the air. Plan on staying cozy inside as the day continues to unfold, using your free time to take care of any chores that have piled up around you. Consider performing a house cleansing or taking a salt bath later tonight, when Luna shares a sweet exchange with revolutionary Uranus. '),(220,'2022-12-23',7,'horoscope','Kick up the heels of your bunny slippers as the year’s second Capricorn new moon lands in your domestic fourth house. (And this one is a potent supermoon.) The most powerful urge you may experience is to feather your nest, whether with a new art print or some blingy ornaments. If Chateau Libra could stand a deep clean, hire a service as a holiday gift for yourself. This galvanizing lunar lift can forebode a move for some Libras, but don’t rush into anything. These beams will be in effect for up to six months. '),(221,'2022-12-24',7,'horoscope','Get excited because this is going to be one great day! Everything will go your way. It will seem as if you simply can\'t lose. At work, team members look to you as the leader. At home, family members express gratitude and affection. You may be tempted to try this luck at the casino, but don\'t be impulsive. You\'re already a winner. You\'ve earned this shining moment'),(222,'2022-12-24',7,'horoscope','The Capricorn moon crosses over Venus this morning, sweet Libra, helping you feel refreshed and balanced as you begin the day. Meanwhile, chatty Mercury blows a kiss to dreamy Neptune, bringing a whimsy to your mind that\'s perfect for lounging at home. These vibes can also help you center your heart, allowing you to resolve any issues that have been weighing on you recently. Consider throwing out unwanted items when Luna crosses over Pluto, encouraging you to purge your space. You\'ll notice a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Aquarius, bringing out your playful side. '),(223,'2022-12-24',7,'horoscope','Your ego could be bruised today, perhaps time to make a compromise to appease a loved one. Try to stay calm during a hectic day at work. Not a good day to disagree with the boss. You may invest time and money in home improvements, but don\\\'t argue about the costs involved. Lucky Colour: Chrome. Lucky Number: 4.'),(224,'2022-12-25',7,'horoscope','You\'ll be in an extroverted and fun-loving mood today, dear Libra, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and your solar fifth house. This luminary placement will also ask you to nurture your friendships, so be sure to spread some love around. You\'ll feel motivated by optimism and passion later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, and divine inspiration can help you see the path ahead with more clarity. Unfortunately, the vibe may get a little tense as the day comes to a close and the moon squares off with Uranus, though you\'ll want to avoid power struggles. '),(225,'2022-12-25',7,'horoscope','Now isn\'t the time to prove to people that you\'re the boss, Libra. They would surely become defensive. You\'re much better off taking a sensitive, nurturing approach on a day like today. Focus your fire internally and use it to drive your own engine. Don\'t run over anyone else in the process or try to run their engine for them.'),(226,'2022-12-25',7,'horoscope','Your rising expenses which will crop up suddenly will be a cause of concern for you. you just need to remain focused and get along with the things. Keeping your financial condition in mind you will talk to your family members to curtail unnecessary expenses. Sweet and sour experiences will be useful in future. You will also have to understand this fact very well that our desires and endless and there is no end. Government employees will put lot of hard work and labor and complete their work in time. You can also plan a business trip. Travel will be smooth. You will also plan to start a new business with your partners. You will also meet lot of new persons connected to your work\n\n'),(227,'2022-12-26',7,'horoscope','You may be forced to do battle with your insecurities today, dear Libra, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect to the healing asteroid, Chiron. Feeling jealous of others will only accentuate these sentiments, making it important that you stay focused on healing and finding happiness within. Luckily, the Aquarius moon and Saturn will join forces to boost your ego, especially if you channel your focus toward professional ambitions or carving out a name for yourself. The vibe will shift later tonight when the moon enters Pisces, helping you regroup and get organized in the coming days. '),(228,'2022-12-26',7,'horoscope','There\'s a lethargic pace to the day that might leave you frustrated, Libra. It may seem as if things aren\'t progressing as quickly as you\'d like. Don\'t be seduced by the idea that everything needs to get done sooner. Faster isn\'t necessarily better. Focus on quality and efficiency. Examine what could be considered wasteful action. Streamline your daily routine.'),(229,'2022-12-26',7,'horoscope','Simmer down! You want to tune out the outer world and listen for messages from your muse today as the moon winks at structured Saturn in Aquarius and your fifth house of creativity and self-expression. If you’ve been taking your talents for granted, it’s time to get a little more serious about them. Withhold judgment for now and just start devoting a few hours a week (and more on weekends) to pursuing your craft—whatever it may be. Aim high, and make art your priority.'),(230,'2022-12-27',7,'horoscope','Your routines will bring you a sense of comfort this morning, dear Libra, as the Pisces moon blows a kiss to the sun. Use this energy to approach the day with efficiency as the stars help you blow through your to-do list. Try not to get carried away with your fantasies later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars. These vibes could cause you to overshoot, making it important that you set reasonable goals, so be sure to focus on your jumping-off points rather than the desired results. Meanwhile, Venus connects with Neptune, allowing you to see the steps to manifest your dreams. '),(231,'2022-12-27',7,'horoscope','You tend to think of yourself as a lone warrior, Libra. Today your efforts over the last few weeks pay off. You\'ve found your place in a group of people. You may even call it a family. You now have a place to come home to, whether it\'s to celebrate your victories or lick your wounds. If you could just open up to other people, you\'d soon find that you have more than one safe haven.'),(232,'2022-12-27',7,'horoscope','Ready to give a bad habit the heave-ho, Libra? That’s not an overnight mission to crush, but you can get a running start today as the Pisces moon circulates through your wellness realm. Approach this from a positive angle rather than a punitive one by thinking “more of this” instead of “less of that.” Recommit to wellness routines that worked for you in the past—and that you actually enjoy. Maybe it’s African dance or mat Pilates, eating a plant-based diet or going Paleo. Small gestures will pave the way for the creation of positive lifestyle habits that you can stick to for the long haul, Libra.'),(233,'2022-12-28',7,'horoscope','Do something nice for your body today, dear Libra, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs wellness. Focus on finding ways to release stress once afternoon emerges, and Luna aligns with ethereal Neptune, giving your cares a chance to melt away. Good vibes will continue to flow later in the day, thanks to a sweet exchange between Venus and Neptune, encouraging you to embrace luxury from the comfort of home. Consider performing a house cleansing or blessing before the day comes to a close, and Pluto becomes active in our skies. '),(234,'2022-12-28',7,'horoscope',' It\'s time to take some time out of your busy day for your personal life, Libra. One of your family members or friends may need to talk to you, and you need to listen attentively to what they have to say. You need to use all your wonderful energy to get down to the heart of the matter. Who knows? You may discover some hidden treasures along the way.'),(235,'2022-12-28',7,'horoscope','If you’ve been feeling less than 100 percent lately, stop playing martyr or pretending this will just go away by itself. Today, the sensitive moon drifts through your sixth house of wellness and self-care. Pause for the cause of your own happiness! Get an appointment on the books with your doctor, dentist, acupuncturist or healing practitioner, stat. Those little aches, pains and energy crashes are like a light going off on your dashboard. A dab of prevention now can get you back in balance'),(236,'2022-12-29',7,'horoscope','The stars will conspire to elevate your love life this morning, sweet Libra, as the Aries moon and Jupiter join forces in the sector of your chart that governs matters of the heart. If you\'re currently coupled up, use this energy to nurture and appreciate the bond you and your sweetie share. If you\'re currently on the hunt for a partner, be sure to let the universe know what you want in a mate. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus cross paths in Capricorn, asking you to dedicate a bit of time and perhaps some money to upgrading your space. '),(237,'2022-12-29',7,'horoscope','The planetary aspects are going to have a big impact on you today, Libra. This isn\'t the time to fear the future. Rather, it\'s a time to make it happen. The action you take right now will be instrumental in your future. Will there be enough of us walking toward the future? Libra will be at the head of the pack in any case, as always.'),(238,'2022-12-29',7,'horoscope','You know the drill when it comes to emotions, Libra: You can run, but you can’t hide. And that goes double starting today as Mercury turns retrograde in your sensitive fourth house of home and family. Between now and January 18, gentleness with your tender heart is required. Whatever you’ve avoided could bubble up, demanding to be processed. Some of it may be tied to ancient pain from family trauma, but try not to get lost in figuring out “why.” Instead, give yourself permission to have an ugly cry or to vent anger to a therapist (maybe as you take a bat to a mattress) and REALLY work the energy out of your system. That raw type of healing will feel profound.'),(239,'2022-12-30',7,'horoscope','A sweetness will hang in the air today, dear Libra, as the moon continues its journey through Aries and the sector of your chart that governs love. Be sure to open your heart to the many joys our universe provides, and allow yourself to temporarily forget your worries and fears. Look for ways to bring your creative ideas into the material realms Luna blows a kiss to pragmatic Saturn during the evening hours. Unfortunately, the vibe could get a little intense later tonight when Luna squares off with Mercury, threatening to accelerate conflict within your domestic sphere or family life. '),(240,'2022-12-30',7,'horoscope',' There\'s a need for decisive action today, Libra, and you\'re the one fit for the job. Strong wills and forceful opinions will win out. Others aren\'t likely to be easily manipulated. Everyone has a voice, and they won\'t be afraid to use it. Make sure that you speak up on your behalf or your best interests may be lost. Stand up for yourself. It\'s now or never.'),(241,'2022-12-30',7,'horoscope','How about getting an early start to that whole midnight-kiss tradition? Your relationship house is lit by today\'s Aries moon. Someone with long-term potential could slip into your 2022 memory book, just in the nick of time! If you\'re feeling feisty yourself, today\'s flirty energy emboldens you to make the first move. Already attached? No need to wait until tomorrow to celebrate the turn of the calendar. Tonight, while it’s still possible to get a reservation, slip off for a dinner date and follow with, ahem, other stress-releasing activities.'),(242,'2022-12-31',7,'horoscope','You\'ll feel eager for change and personal upgrades today, dear Libra, as the moon moves into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs transformation. Unfortunately, these vibes may move more slowly than you\'d like, making it important that you are patient with your progress. Work with these vibes by taking small steps toward the future you want, and don\'t be afraid to financially invest in these shifts. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto form a celestial union in the sky, inspiring you to freshen up your space. Whether it\'s time to purge your closet, repaint the living room, or invest in new cookware-- now is the time to update your home for the new year. '),(243,'2022-12-31',7,'horoscope','There is a chance that somebody near to you can steal your ideas to advance their own careers. So, be careful sharing new ideas with anyone. You have to keep a sharp eye out or your own interest at this time. Do not share knowledge with your colleagues even if you have known them for a long time. Patience during this time will help to reveal your true well-wishers to you.'),(244,'2022-12-31',7,'horoscope','Today, you will be in a mishmash of emotions and feelings. Also, there are chances of accumulated feelings finding an outlet.\n\nYour capacity for emotional display may take people by surprise. However, you will also enjoy the higher responsibilities reposed on you'),(245,'2022-12-21',8,'horoscope','If you’ve been keeping your ideas—and opinions and feelings—to yourself, Scorpio, it’s time to open the vault! Today, the expressive Sun commences a four-week visit through circumspect Capricorn and your communication corner, helping you find just the right words for any occasion. You seldom need to be reminded to trust your instincts, but a word to the wise never hurts. This cycle is great for brainstorming new ways to get your message out there—with your favorite fellow innovators!'),(246,'2022-12-21',8,'horoscope','It\'s time to get serious about turning your ideas into reality, dear Scorpio, as the sun enters Capricorn and your solar third house. These vibes are all about backing up your thoughts with tangible action, especially when it comes to expanding your knowledge base or improving upon your professional standing. You\'ll also notice that others are more responsive to your words, making it a good time to express your goals and needs. Give yourself permission to slow down and nurture your body this evening when the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Chiron, asking you to prioritize wellness. '),(247,'2022-12-21',8,'horoscope','Your emotions may be more in tune with the world around you today, Scorpio. You could even feel a bit psychic. Go with your hunches. You will find that rational thinking may not be the best way to handle situations right now. Be the sensitive one who feels things before acting. Discuss the issues with others and combine your resources for a more powerful alliance.'),(248,'2022-12-22',8,'horoscope','No matter how busy your day is, find time to nurture a few of your most meaningful relationships. This doesn’t mean the easiest or most fun; sometimes, Scorpio, it’s the people we struggle most with yet can’t seem to extricate ourselves from who have the most to teach us. (After all, people, especially difficult ones, are our greatest mirrors.) As heart-stirring Venus aligns with scientific Uranus in your partnership zone, pay attention to the feelings that others evoke in you. There are some big teachings in that data!'),(249,'2022-12-22',8,'horoscope','Love could manifest in unexpected places today, dear Scorpio, as Venus and Uranus share a sweet exchange in the sky. These vibes are perfect for breaking the ice with anyone you\'ve been eying lately, though a few new admirers may reveal themselves as well. Meanwhile, the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to stabilizing Saturn, helping you connect with the beauty and your sense of gratitude. Unfortunately, your self-awareness could take a hit when Luna squares off with hazy Neptune this afternoon, making it a good time to focus on your composure. The vibe will shift this evening when the moon enters Sagittarius, amplifying your voice throughout the next two days. '),(250,'2022-12-22',8,'horoscope','Your sensitivity is strong today, Scorpio. You will find that your perception of situations is right on target with the truth of the matter. Keep in mind that in order to be successful, you won\'t need to strong-arm anyone into doing what you want. More than likely you will be able to accomplish more just by tuning in to your receptive, gentle nature.'),(251,'2022-12-23',8,'horoscope','Think globally but save your best acts for the local scene! Today, a new supermoon in Capricorn powers up your third house of socializing and hometown happenings. Even if it’s cold outside, this is a great opportunity to meet kindred souls in the ‘hood who are doing things you’re interested in. You don’t have to be a mere observer or participant, either! Talk to people and see where help is needed. It could be that a shopkeeper could use the very skills or products you’re trying to market. And if you’re single, there could well be a fringe benefit in the offing! '),(252,'2022-12-23',8,'horoscope','Think before speaking today, dear Scorpio, as the Capricorn new moon activates the sector of your chart that governs communication. People will take you seriously right now, which means you\'ll want to be strategic in how you use your words. These vibes are also perfect for starting new educational journeys, marking the ideal moment to enroll in a class or pick up a fresh hobby. Surprising information could change the course of your love life this evening, when Luna connects with the nodes of fate before entering a sweet exchange with Uranus, which could make or break your relationship'),(253,'2022-12-23',8,'horoscope','This is a day for rest and relaxation, Scorpio. Take advantage of the calm atmosphere to center yourself and focus on what\'s important in your life. You\'ve been going at full speed, and it\'s possible that your family feels somewhat neglected. Spend some quality time with loved ones, if possible. They miss you and will welcome your company. Other concerns come and go, but family is forever.'),(254,'2022-12-24',8,'horoscope','This is a good day for quiet contemplation, Scorpio. You may have worried about finances lately, but there\'s no longer any need to concern yourself. All signs indicate that your financial fortunes are about to change. You\'ve been working hard and should reap some rewards. Today\'s aspects suggest that you will. Enjoy your newfound peace of mind, but don\'t go out and use the credit cards in celebration'),(255,'2022-12-24',8,'horoscope','Take a moment to touch base with your heart while tapping into your gratitude this morning, dear Scorpio, as the Capricorn moon crosses over sweet Venus. Meanwhile, Mercury blows a kiss to dreamy Neptune, bringing a rush of inspiration to your psyche. Use this energy to get creative within your passion projects, allowing your artistic side to take over. Profound thoughts will find you this evening when Luna cozies up to Pluto, giving you the strength to verbally cut ties with anyone or anything that\'s been causing you grief. You\'ll feel a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Aquarius, putting you in the mood for a relaxing night at home.'),(256,'2022-12-24',8,'horoscope','Problems with colleagues are likely. At work, it looks like you are in for new phase, with your team beginning to rely heavily on you. Of course you can never say \\\'no,\\\' but don\\\'t stretch yourself thin. You can ask for favours but don\\\'t take others for granted. Be diplomatic but stern. Lucky Colour: Amber. Lucky Number: 7.'),(257,'2022-12-25',8,'horoscope','A buzz and excitement will fill your home today, dear Scorpio, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss. If you\'re observing the holiday with your family, be sure to add some flare to the mix, honoring your traditions while adding a fresh spin. Don\'t be afraid to access your sentimental side later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, helping you deepen the bonds with your loved ones. Try not to stay up past your bedtime, or a square between the moon and Uranus could trigger moodiness.'),(258,'2022-12-25',8,'horoscope',' This is a favorable day for you to deal with intimate and sensitive issues, Scorpio. You will be in comfortable situations that allow you to express what you believe. There\'s no need to hold back, because people will have a greater understanding of what it is you feel. You combine deep emotions with mental clarity and you\'re able to see through to the truth in other people\'s words'),(259,'2022-12-25',8,'horoscope','You will make impossible work possible through your talent, creatively and dedication. You will also get lot of appreciation for it. You will also get success in love affairs. You can also get promoted in your job/business. You will also make new friends. You will also be socially active. And interact with lot of people. Those who are in politics, media, sports and entertainment industry will do very well and also get lot of name and fame. Some misunderstanding that you had with your partner will get removed. Your long standing work that was struck up will get completed. You will have growth in your business. Legal matters will get resolved. You will also solve property disputes\n\n'),(260,'2022-12-26',8,'horoscope','You may become burnt out with the daily grind today, dear Scorpio, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. Feelings of boredom and elevated stress levels will accentuate these sentiments, though catering to your health and sense of wellness can help pull you through your to-do list. Luckily, you\'ll feel in control of your emotions as the Aquarius moon cozies up to Saturn, helping you find the endurance to persevere. Good vibes will flow as the day comes to a close and Luna enters Pisces, encouraging you to access your imagination throughout the next two days'),(261,'2022-12-26',8,'horoscope','This is a terrific day for you to accomplish a lot, Scorpio. You may feel restricted in your emotions and unable to make certain deep-level connections, but don\'t worry about it. If the time doesn\'t feel right to engage in deep conversation, don\'t push it. Concentrate on the things that you need to get done personally and professionally.'),(262,'2022-12-26',8,'horoscope','Who’s in control here, Scorpio: you—or your emotions? Today, when the sensitive moon mashes up with restrained Saturn in your fourth house of sentimentality, it’s a coin toss. Normally you keep those intense feelings carefully labeled and tucked away for (occasional) display. But thanks to this planetary pairing, the waterworks could switch on without warning. Go ahead and feel what you’re feeling, but stop short of actually telling the boss how to do her job'),(263,'2022-12-27',8,'horoscope','Your popularity will benefit from a cosmic boost this morning, dear Scorpio, thanks to a sweet exchange between the sun and moon. Lean into these supportive vibes by using your voice, as your charisma and wit can help you win the favor of others. However, you\'ll need to slow down later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars, making it a good time to lay low. The nodes of fate will be active this evening, asking you to think creatively about the future. Meanwhile, Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, encouraging you to believe in your dreams.'),(264,'2022-12-27',8,'horoscope','You love the creative process, Scorpio. Even watering your plants or painting a picture will give you a feeling of joy. If this month you get a chance to finish a project that you really care about, you will be satisfied with the results. And you will be surprised to see people react positively. It\'s OK to be proud of yourself'),(265,'2022-12-27',8,'horoscope','Work, chores, family obligations: You’re in the mood for exactly NONE of these things today! And that\'s perfectly all right, Scorpio. As the moon alights in Pisces and your playful, celebratory fifth house, creative projects are clamoring for your attention. At the very least, try to do the things that will make you happy and reduce your stress levels. You might prefer to go the self-pampering route by booking a facial or trying on some outfits for NYE. Spend time with people who lift your spirits. Their energy can be contagious! '),(266,'2022-12-28',8,'horoscope','Don\'t be afraid to embrace your wild side, dear Scorpio, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and the sector of your chart that governs ego, drama, and fun. These vibes are perfect for getting imaginative with your image, especially when Luna cozies up to Neptune this afternoon. A passionate and romantic energy will find you later in the afternoon when the moon blows a kiss to Venus, so be sure to invest some TLC into that special someone. Your thoughts will be profound as the day comes to a close, and Pluto is activated by the moon. '),(267,'2022-12-28',8,'horoscope','Today is a good day to clarify your life, Scorpio. You may have understood lately that it\'s useless to undertake anything new when you\'re confused. You\'ve figured out that all it takes to get out of that state is to take care of yourself, eat better, get more sleep, or take a vacation. Your mind will be sufficiently rested today to deal with all the problems that come your way'),(268,'2022-12-28',8,'horoscope','Do you know the difference between healthy and unhealthy fantasy, Scorpio? If it keeps you “up!” and doesn’t interfere with your day-to-day life, it’s probably a positive thing. But if you find yourself spiraling and obsessing about losing control, pay attention to that red flag. Today, as the dreamy Pisces moon drifts through your romantic fifth house, examine how realistic you are being about the person, place or thing that’s occupying your thoughts. You love your highs, but if they’re always offset by despairing lows, it’s time for a more grounded approach.'),(269,'2022-12-29',8,'horoscope','You\'ll feel as though you can take on the world today, dear Scorpio, as the Aries moon and Jupiter collide in your solar sixth house. These vibes are perfect for chipping away at your goals, as the effort you showcase today will have positive and lasting impacts tomorrow. Feel free to speak honestly and from a place of love as the hours continue to pass, while Mercury and Venus align in the sky. Take a moment to meditate on any people or situations who might be holding you back as Luna blows a kiss to Mars later in the afternoon. '),(270,'2022-12-29',8,'horoscope',' People are more alike than we think, especially on days like today that mean virtually the same thing to everyone. Some incredible changes have taken place in the world and its economic and social systems. Now is the time to think about what the next few years have in store. Do you have any ideas? Try to articulate them'),(271,'2022-12-29',8,'horoscope','Do the words escape you, Scorpio? That predicament may be more of a constant than your articulate sign prefers over the coming three weeks as messenger Mercury retrogrades through your third house of communication. When you find yourself flustered or at a loss for what to say, don’t force yourself to issue a statement. Instead, ask for clarification, and don’t stop until you truly understand what people are trying to express. This is the best conflict-de-escalation policy possible!'),(272,'2022-12-30',8,'horoscope','The moon continues its journey through fiery Aries and your solar sixth house today, dear Scorpio, helping you wrap up your professional to-do list before the weekend kicks off. Just remember to nurture your body with healthy foods and plenty of water, or you could end up hitting a wall. The stars will ask you to bring order to your home this evening when Luna blows a kiss to responsible Saturn. Watch out for mental chatter or miscommunications later tonight when the moon squares off with Mercury, thickening the air with a tension that could result in arguments and personal anxiety. '),(273,'2022-12-30',8,'horoscope','There may be tension and opposition today, Scorpio, so be prepared. It could seem like everyone wants to rattle your cage. Stand strong. There are forceful opinions crying out to be heard. The more stubborn you are, the harder it will be for important information to flow freely. Protect your interests by standing your ground, but make sure you don\'t step on other people\'s toes in the process'),(274,'2022-12-30',8,'horoscope','It\'s not even January yet, but today’s Aries moon has you in a mission-oriented mindset. Squeeze the last bit of industrious energy into your 2022 by tying up at least one loose end. Skip the Friday-night crowds and hit the gym before you retreat to your lair asap. Late tomorrow, your social urges will return. Before you can find your love for others, you need to devote some uninterrupted time to yourself. Fill the tub with scented bubbles and binge-watch a series on your laptop while you soak. Ahhh.'),(275,'2022-12-31',8,'horoscope','The vibe will be light, sweet, and harmonious today, dear Scorpio, as the moon migrates into sensual Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs love. Use this energy as an excuse to unapologetically pamper yourself, as the universes will support your mission for relaxation and luxury. If you\'re in a relationship, consider bringing your sweetie along for the ride, nurturing your relationship with yummy foods or perhaps a couple\'s massage. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto align in the sky, allowing you to seriously discuss what\'s in your heart, and what the future of your romantic entanglements might look like in the new year.'),(276,'2022-12-31',8,'horoscope','Today you may have some problem with your transport. If you are going for an important work, double check your alternative mode of transport and keep a backup plan ready. You may be a little agitated from inside. But do not lose your cool as it is just a short phase and will pass by easily. Spend time with your family.'),(277,'2022-12-31',8,'horoscope','Today will be a day full of focus and a clear thought process. The clarity of thought you have has been acquired over a period of time, and that could make all the difference.\n\nA crisp application of thoughts to ideas and actions will bring much appreciation from bosses and peers'),(278,'2022-12-21',9,'horoscope','Well, THAT was fun! For the past month, the shimmering Sun has been beaming through your sign, lighting up your life and presumably setting your social calendar on fire. Today, el Sol downshifts into structured Capricorn and your second house of finances. This is a great time to catch up with yourself and let the coffers refill. While holiday season can be tough on a budget, if most of your presents have already been purchased, now you can look forward to four weeks of enjoying the best things in life—which P.S. aren’t necessarily going to be “things.”'),(279,'2022-12-21',9,'horoscope','The universe will ask you to slow down and find your center today, dear Archer, as the sun moves out of your sign and into stabilizing Capricorn. This solar placement can also bring financial gains your way, making it a great time to plant seeds for the future. A rush of playful energy will wash over you as the sun and Jupiter align. However, you\'ll want to be mindful of your audience, as it would be easy to lose touch with your self-awareness. Plan on dedicating your evening to a passion project or creative outlet when Luna blows a kiss to Chiron. '),(280,'2022-12-21',9,'horoscope','You might second-guess yourself today, Sagittarius. Voices in your head are louder than usual, and you could be the one putting the brakes on your own train. Your intuition is trying to break through. See what you can do to slow down the chatter that continues to dictate the narrative throughout the day. Do more feeling instead of thinking. Give your mind a rest.'),(281,'2022-12-22',9,'horoscope','Your hedonistic sign may be pulled toward some indulgences today, but if they’re good for your body, mind or soul (or, ideally, at least two), then go ahead and spoil yourself! Decadent Venus is firing up your sensual (yet practical) second house and is in a sweet sync-up with rebellious Uranus in your wellness sector. These two only align twice a year, and when they do, good luck resisting temptation. As long as it’s beneficial, there’s nothing to feel remotely guilty about!'),(282,'2022-12-22',9,'horoscope','The stars will ask you to invest in luxury and wellness today, dear Archer, as Venus shares a sweet exchange with Uranus. These vibes are perfect for breaking the mold of your current routine, making it a good time to schedule a massage or finally enroll in yoga classes. You\'ll have a chance to speak your truth with authority when the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Saturn. So, be sure to use your voice. Unfortunately, your emotions could start to cloud your judgment as afternoon rolls in and Luna squares off with Neptune, bringing a haze to the collective. '),(283,'2022-12-22',9,'horoscope','You may feel a bit confused today. It might seem as if the wind has suddenly been taken out of your sails. Don\'t get discouraged by the slow weightiness of the day. Take the opportunity to relax and recharge your batteries. Do a bit of inward reflection as opposed to outer-directed movement. The most valuable lesson to learn is patience. Remind yourself of this throughout the day.'),(284,'2022-12-23',9,'horoscope','You won’t have to squint to see your ship coming in on the horizon, Archer! Today, the year’s second Capricorn new moon—also a powerful supermoon—lands in your second house of finances and security. This lunar lift will help you get a handle on your spending habits and places you’re “leaking” your hard-earned funds. But the best way to motivate yourself to prioritize saving money is to have clear and immediate goals. Need a new car, hoping to put a down payment on a house or maybe take a dream vacation in the new year? Figure out your magic number, how many weeks you have to accumulate that, crunch the numbers—and then tighten your belt as needed.'),(285,'2022-12-23',9,'horoscope','The universe will ask you to plant seeds for your financial future, dear Archer, as the Capricorn new moon activates the sector of your chart that governs money and security. These vibes are also perfect for tapping into your gratitude, so be sure to acknowledge the beauty that surrounds you. Though you\'ll be eager to see growth within your circumstances, the energy at play will move slowly, which means opportunities that arise right now may not unfold as quickly as you\'d like. Take a moment to nurture your health before the day comes to a close, when Luna shares a sweet aspect with Uranus.'),(286,'2022-12-23',9,'horoscope','You won’t have to squint to see your ship coming in on the horizon, Archer! Today, the year’s second Capricorn new moon—also a powerful supermoon—lands in your second house of finances and security. This lunar lift will help you get a handle on your spending habits and places you’re “leaking” your hard-earned funds. But the best way to motivate yourself to prioritize saving money is to have clear and immediate goals. Need a new car, hoping to put a down payment on a house or maybe take a dream vacation in the new year? Figure out your magic number, how many weeks you have to accumulate that, crunch the numbers—and then tighten your belt as needed.'),(287,'2022-12-24',9,'horoscope','Sagittarius, you\'re bound to enjoy this day! It\'s full of possibilities and opportunities. It may begin routinely, but keep your eyes and ears open for hints of change. Your new adventure may come about in a mundane way. You might meet someone in line at the store who becomes a business partner. Or maybe you will meet a romantic interest at the ATM. Adventure is all around. Trust that you will find it'),(288,'2022-12-24',9,'horoscope','Consider investing in a luxury item for your space this morning, when the Capricorn moon crosses over beautifying Venus. You\'ll have an opportunity to eloquently express your emotions as the day continues to unfold, dear Archer, thanks to a sweet exchange between communicative Mercury and ethereal Neptune. These vibes can also help you feel secure within your heart, especially if you discuss any fears that have been plaguing your mind. You\'ll feel a shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Aquarius, encouraging you to speak honestly and earnestly throughout the next two and a half days. '),(289,'2022-12-24',9,'horoscope','Socializing with clients or colleagues not favourable today. Avoid people and situations that could lead to stress and working overtime. A good day to keep a low profile, and watch your boss being positive towards your work. Lucky Colour: Sapphire. Lucky Number: 1'),(290,'2022-12-25',9,'horoscope','The weirdo that lives within you will stir from its slumber today, dear Archer, as the moon continues its journey through eccentric Aquarius. This luminary placement could inspire you to say some truly wild things, but if your heart is in the right place your words will be well received. Opportunities to flirt and rekindle the passion in your love life could come into play when Luna blows a kiss to Mars later in the afternoon, so be sure to squeeze your sweetie extra tight. Unfortunately, a stressful vibe will permeate the air later tonight, making it important that you maintain a patient and kind demeanor'),(291,'2022-12-25',9,'horoscope',' There\'s a very heavy atmosphere around you that might feel stifling, Sagittarius. Situations are cropping up that urge you to think practically with regard to your emotions. You will find that things go much more smoothly if you slow down and think about a situation before you proceed. Make sure you consider all the choices and what their effects will be on other people'),(292,'2022-12-25',9,'horoscope','Money and wealth will keep coming. You will have financial gains. It is time of great profits in your business. You will do well in your profession. Those who were planning a job change and were in two minds about it can now take an appropriate decision. Your income will rise. Hence you can invest it in a good place. You will also get along very well with your life partner. He/she may disagree with you on a matter or two. But that will not bother you much. You will have apprehension in your mind about your image coming under a cloud at your workplace. But your fears are unfounded. In fact, your colleagues respect you a lot.\n\n'),(293,'2022-12-26',9,'horoscope','The Aquarius moon cozies up to responsible Saturn in the sector of your chart that governs communication this morning, dear Archer, helping you strategize and discuss your plans from an innovative yet pragmatic headspace. Take a moment to brainstorm solutions to your problems, looking for ways to tighten your grip on the future you desire most. However, you\'ll want to give your big, beautiful mind a rest as the day comes to a close and Luna migrates into Pisces. These vibes are all about unwinding, asking you to nurture yourself by laying low from the comfort of home.'),(294,'2022-12-26',9,'horoscope','Slow down a bit today and do some planning. There\'s a steady, grounded mood that will help bring your thoughts and actions down to Earth. The wind may not be filling your sails as much as you\'d like, but you can use this to your advantage. The underlying reservation in people\'s attitudes and opinions will aid you quite a bit. Eliminate the fluff and concentrate on what\'s real'),(295,'2022-12-26',9,'horoscope','Today, as the emo moon teams up with dour Saturn in your thoughtful third house, you might only be able to see the clouds and not the silver linings. Even if you can’t change the situation, you CAN change your reaction to it. You can certainly take a few small, proactive steps in the direction you want to steer this. And if nothing helps, table it until tomorrow, when today’s “shadow work” paves the way for some fresh insight'),(296,'2022-12-27',9,'horoscope','The Pisces moon blows a kiss to the sun this morning, dear Sagittarius, lifting your spirits and sense of gratitude. These vibes are perfect for connecting with your space, so be sure to show your home some love. Unfortunately, emotions will run high later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with passionate Mars. Matters of the heart could become particularly distressing, making it important to monitor your emotions when it comes to love. Meanwhile, Venus shares a sweet exchange with dreamy Neptune, giving you permission to escape into a world of luxury-- so go ahead and spoil yourself!'),(297,'2022-12-27',9,'horoscope',' Sagittarius, your lighthearted attitude has given you a reputation as an eternal teenager. But levity is also a sign of a very wise person, a person who knows how to laugh at their wisdom. Whether you realize it or not, you can get involved in a serious relationship without losing your lightheartedness. If you\'re already in a committed relationship, you know how true this is'),(298,'2022-12-27',9,'horoscope','Cultural curiosity has led you to far-flung corners of the earth, but here’s a news alert. You can get your fix from Sag Central too. Today, an inwardly focused Pisces moon sets up base camp in your domestic fourth house, turning your attention to things you can do in your fleece-lined slippers. You\'ll be particularly attuned to your surroundings, so follow your intuitive inspiration! Does your space feel like your sanctuary—or could it use some TLC? Start with a gentle decluttering mission––maybe just a micro one to get rid of the winter sweaters that remind you of a dreary 2020? '),(299,'2022-12-28',9,'horoscope','Devote your day to nurturing your heart and most valued relationships, dear Archer, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and your solar fourth house. Emotional exchanges will also prove to be quite valuable, making it a good time to open up with someone you trust. The energy in your home will be especially peaceful this afternoon when Luna cozies up to Neptune. Plan on indulging in a bath or your favorite self-care routine later in the afternoon, as the moon blows a kiss to harmonious Venus. Consider tidying up your space later tonight, when Luna connects with Pluto. '),(300,'2022-12-28',9,'horoscope','Are you going to be available to other people today? Someone in your entourage may need to confide in you. If the superficiality of the exchange bothers you, you will understand what the atmosphere of today is all about! Yes, you\'re available, but not for just anything. You\'re in no mood to waste time at the moment'),(301,'2022-12-28',9,'horoscope','Don’t freak out if you can’t flap your social butterfly wings today, Sagittarius. Even your high-flying sign needs to come in for a landing every now and then. And today, as the solitary Pisces moon nestles into your domesticity zone, take a step backward and enjoy a bit of cocooning. Slip into comfy clothes, dim the lighting, cook up something nourishing and have a blessed night IN, alone or with your favorite mellow people.'),(302,'2022-12-29',9,'horoscope','Your vibe will be larger than life this morning, dear Sagittarius, as the moon migrates into Aries and cozies up to expansive Jupiter. These vibes are all about standing in your truth, so don\'t be afraid to take life by the reins with authenticity and no apologies. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus will be in alliance, making it a good time to reinforce yourself and your romantic partner through praise and positive words. Passion and romance will fill the air later tonight when Luna blows a kiss to fiery Mars. So, be sure to invest in people or activities that light you up!'),(303,'2022-12-29',9,'horoscope','Today is an inspirational day for you, fast thinking Sagittarius. Let those visions come to you, process them, and try to verbalize them. A lot of information and electricity is in the air, and you should have no problem picking up on it. Open up your channels for the best reception. Have a notepad handy to jot down all your insights'),(304,'2022-12-29',9,'horoscope','Real change happens incrementally, but good luck telling that to a Sagittarius charging ahead on a mission! But as you barrel toward your 2023 goals, know this: Mercury is turning retrograde today, backing up through your pragmatic second house until January 18. Since haste CAN make waste during this three-week cycle, make sure you’ve thought plans through thoroughly before you shell out cash or commit to any time-consuming projects. If you “need” to do anything splashy over the coming few weeks, think in terms of micro-moves instead of long-term obligations.'),(305,'2022-12-30',9,'horoscope','It\'s okay if you want to be a bit \"extra\"\" today'),(306,'2022-12-30',9,'horoscope','What ails you now can be eliminated if you\'re willing to stand up and say exactly what needs to be said, Sagittarius. Going with the flow may be an easy route to follow, but it might not always take you down a path that leads to the fulfillment of your dreams. Be a bit more aggressive about your position today and outwardly project yourself as the true master of your destiny'),(307,'2022-12-30',9,'horoscope','More, more, more? That\'s the way your expansive sign usually rolls! So while the year might be winding down, today\'s expansive Aries moon increases your appetite for life. Go on and be a bit more decadent, Sagittarius, because when it comes to the stars, tonight’s festive mood could outdo your NYE celebrations. Splurge on a round of cheer for your friends or to treat yourself to a dopamine-bright party outfit that will photograph like a dream tomorrow night! Life is meant to be celebrated.'),(308,'2022-12-31',9,'horoscope','The moon moves into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs wellness today, dear Archer, asking you to prioritize your health in the new year. Whether you need to implement a more consistent sleep schedule, cut back on your vices, or exercise more, now is the time to pledge your allegiance to such changes in 2023. However, it\'ll be important that you give yourself plenty of time to meet such goals, as Venus and Pluto align in your solar second house. While this celestial exchange will certainly promote the idea of transformation, the energy will move slowly, and so should you!'),(309,'2022-12-31',9,'horoscope','You are feeling rather disorganized and chaotic today. Your thoughts tend to flow in a number of directions today. The result is that you will not be able to wrap up any project today. You need to focus. Try some mental exercise and do not consult with other people as contradictory advice would tend to confuse you even further'),(310,'2022-12-31',9,'horoscope','Life is bubbling within you, and you shall be in a hyper-elevated state of bliss today. Your high-spirits and energy will inspire you to perform at your best.\n\nMoreover, your inner voice will be loud and bellowing. Make the most of this superb day.'),(311,'2022-12-21',10,'horoscope','Ready or not, today kicks off your favorite time of the year: Capricorn season! This is your annual hall pass to indulge your deepest desires, pursue your personal passions—and just say no thanks to anything that promises to be dull, dreary or in any way dissatisfying! Your dutiful sign tends to put other people’s needs first, but during YOUR month, you’re urged to take care of numero uno. This solar power surge dials up your confidence, so be ready to take a (calculated) risk and do it!'),(312,'2022-12-21',10,'horoscope','Go ahead and do a happy dance today, dear Capricorn, as the sun enters your sign, ushering in winter and your time to shine. you should feel energized, creative, and adored throughout the coming weeks, as doors open and people rally around to lift you up. Just try not to get overwhelmed by the idea of another candle landing on your cake or a square between the sun and Jupiter could cause you to become emotional and nostalgic. Plan on scheduling some quiet time from the comfort of home this evening when the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to Chiron. '),(313,'2022-12-21',10,'horoscope','Today is excellent for you, Capricorn. You will find that things flow naturally in the very way you\'ve visualized. You might even find that things actually go much better than you had envisioned! Go about your endeavors confidently. The whole world isn\'t out to get you. In fact, people are probably too concerned with themselves to even bother with what you\'re'),(314,'2022-12-22',10,'horoscope','Good luck focusing on those dull-as-dishwater tasks today, Capricorn! Pleasure planet Venus is buzzing through your sign, and a biannual bond with rebellious Uranus in your sensual fifth house could conflate an attraction into a full-blown obsession. Since you may not be able to avoid falling down that rabbit hole, at least attempt to set limits. Give yourself five minutes at a pop to “go there,” with your full intensity. But when the “time\'s up” alarm goes, get back to work!'),(315,'2022-12-22',10,'horoscope','Breaking free from your routine will qualify as the ultimate act of self-care today, dear Capricorn, as sweet Venus shares a supportive exchange with unpredictable Uranus. These vibes will give you the cosmic green light to embrace fun above all else, though creative outlets will also feel particularly appealing. If you\'ve been caught in a rut with your sweetheart lately, use this energy as an excuse to seek new experiences as a team. Unfortunately, confusion and miscommunications could take hold this afternoon when the Sagittarius moon squares off with deceptive Neptune. Luckily, clarity will find you before the day comes to a close and the moon enters your sign. '),(316,'2022-12-22',10,'horoscope',' Today is an excellent day for you, Capricorn. You will be a welcome addition to any crowd. Your delightful nature is at its most active. You have the unique capability to be aggressive about getting what you want without disturbing the flow of the energy around you. People respect and honor your sensitive, nurturing qualities. This will win the game for you.'),(317,'2022-12-23',10,'horoscope','Today is like a personal birthday party for you, regardless of when your actual birth date is! The year’s second new moon in your sign also happens to be an electrifying supermoon, and its influence will fire you up with motivation and passion. No more hesitation: Take on some of your bigger challenges now while you\'ve got a fire blazing in your belly. What dreams can you set in motion that will help you achieve these lofty aspirations? Mark your calendar for July 3, 2023, the day of the corresponding FULL moon in Capricorn—and an ideal goal post for manifestation!'),(318,'2022-12-23',10,'horoscope','The new moon manifests in your sign early this morning, darling Sea-Goat, asking you to meditate on your hopes and aspirations. This luminary will act as one of the most supportive times of the year for you, as the universe conspires to help you reach your goals. Be sure to light a candle and let the other side know where you could use some help, almost as if you were making a wish upon a star. You\'ll feel wired and eager for excitement later tonight when Luna forms a sweet aspect with unpredictable Uranus, marking the ideal moment to break free from the norm. '),(319,'2022-12-23',10,'horoscope','Today is like a personal birthday party for you, regardless of when your actual birth date is! The year’s second new moon in your sign also happens to be an electrifying supermoon, and its influence will fire you up with motivation and passion. No more hesitation: Take on some of your bigger challenges now while you\'ve got a fire blazing in your belly. What dreams can you set in motion that will help you achieve these lofty aspirations? Mark your calendar for July 3, 2023, the day of the corresponding FULL moon in Capricorn—and an ideal goal post for manifestation!'),(320,'2022-12-24',10,'horoscope','Forget about work for a change and focus instead on your love life! This is one area that can really use some attention. There\'s no sense waiting for your partner to do it. It\'s up to you. Why not book a romantic weekend? It will do wonders for your relationship and add spark just by anticipating the fun you will have. Your commitment should mean more than your independence.'),(321,'2022-12-24',10,'horoscope','Allow your whims to guide you this morning, dear Capricorn, as the moon continues its journey through your sign while forming a cosmic alliance with sweet Venus. These vibes are perfect for cuddling up with that special someone, so don\'t feel guilty about sleeping in. Meanwhile, chatty Mercury blows a kiss to ethereal Neptune, blessing your mind with creative visions. You\'ll be in a unique position to enchant others with your words, so don\'t feel guilty about relying on your powers of persuasion. The vibe will shift later tonight when the moon enters Aquarius, putting you in a grounded yet playful mood. '),(322,'2022-12-24',10,'horoscope','Don’t be too dogmatic in your ideas. If you close your mind, you will inevitably shut out some people who could enrich your life in ways you don\\\'t yet understand. You need balance in your life. Your obviously unique way of doing things has caught the eye of someone in a higher position. Lucky Colour: White. Lucky Number: 3'),(323,'2022-12-25',10,'horoscope','You\'ll be in a generous and playful mood today, dear Capricorn, as the moon continues its journey through Aquarius and your solar second house. Though your quirky side is sure to make an appearance, the responsibility of holiday festivities will keep you grounded, especially if you\'re the glue that holds people together. Check in with your body later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, ensuring that you\'re staying hydrated and eating enough to maintain your energy levels. Watch out for tension or insecurities as the day comes to a close and Luna squares off with Uranus'),(324,'2022-12-25',10,'horoscope',' Just when you thought that the whole world was turning on you, Capricorn, things start to come back around. You will find that you don\'t need to hide. In fact, the more you let your true spirit emerge, the more allies you will gain. Your secret ambition to rule your world is becoming a much more attainable goal than you might have thought at first.'),(325,'2022-12-25',10,'horoscope','You need to learn some lessons from mistakes made by you. it is time to move ahead in your life. Your past should not hold you back. Your desires will get fulfilled. However, you will have to take care of your finances. Moving forward with experienced people will prove to be helpful for you. You will also get a good job/business offer. You will make changes to your way of working. You will keep your bosses happy. You will also work hard to manage your house and family. Your life will be back on track. You will witness tensions in your family ties but you will solve them. Some person may help you when you need it most. Those who are single will get marriage proposals.\n\n'),(326,'2022-12-26',10,'horoscope','You may feel a little less patient with your friends and colleagues today, dear Capricorn, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. These sentiments will feel particularly pronounced if you\'re struggling with personal issues or if you\'re tired of helping others clean their own messes. Luckily, a cosmic alliance between the Aquarius moon and Saturn will give you permission to implement boundaries when you need to, so don\'t feel guilty about sending your incoming calls to voicemail. You\'ll feel much more talkative as Luna enters Pisces near the day’s end, activating the sector of your chart that governs communication.'),(327,'2022-12-26',10,'horoscope',' There\'s a call for you to focus on tangible items today, Capricorn. Your emotions may be a bit restricted, but you will find comfort in beautiful, luxurious surroundings. Don\'t be surprised if people are a bit more critical than usual. What they intend as helpful may come across as hurtful. Try to keep a positive spin on things or you may slip down a negative spiral of self-pity.'),(328,'2022-12-26',10,'horoscope','As the end of the fiscal year approaches—and the intuitive moon aligns with your ruler, structured Saturn—visions of bank statements and spreadsheets may be dancing in your head. Whether you’re saving for a specific goal or just trying to pay off your debt in 2023, your mind is on your budget this Boxing Day. Set up an early January appointment with a financial adviser or someone who can help you think pragmatically about your bottom line.'),(329,'2022-12-27',10,'horoscope','Your social interactions will bring forth instant gratification, dear Capricorn, when the sun and moon share a sweet exchange this morning. Use this energy to check in with your buds and colleagues, but try not to let your electronic devices take away from your to-do list. Unfortunately, the temptation to focus on your social life will be pronounced, and a harsh square between Luna and Mars later in the afternoon suggests you may struggle to get caught up at work. Try to get in some journaling this evening when Venus blows a kiss to Neptune, bringing poetry to your words.'),(330,'2022-12-27',10,'horoscope','What changes have there been in your life since this time last year? Think about the events that have taken place. What have you accomplished? What decisions have you made? And most importantly, how much you have grown as a person? Try to make changes by following your intuition. Even though it seems stressful and sometimes painful, change means growth!'),(331,'2022-12-27',10,'horoscope','As today’s tuned-in Pisces moon heats up your third house of hometown happenings, think “locally sourced” and “community-driven.” Has it been a while since you poked around the nearby vintage store or checked out the Pinot selection at that natural wine shop on the corner? Neighborhood venues like these are what make your zip code unique. And if you’re feeling particularly enterprising, see how your talents or services might overlap with the proprietor’s needs. Co-hosting something like a pop-up “shop in a shop” or fund-raising tarot night might be a win-win!'),(332,'2022-12-28',10,'horoscope','You\'ll take on the role of social butterfly today, dear Sea-Goat, as the Pisces moon continues its journey through the sector of your chart that governs communication. You\'ll have an opportunity to inspire others with your visionary ideas this afternoon when Luna cozies up to ethereal Neptune. Try to conversationally nurture your love life later in the afternoon, as the moon and Venus align in our sky. A cleansing energy will find you later tonight when Luna blows a kiss to Pluto, making it a good time to indulge in a relaxing salt bath or smoke cleanse your space'),(333,'2022-12-28',10,'horoscope','You may come in contact with someone today with whom you enjoy a highly emotional exchange. You may even fall in love! Be very attentive to your moods and everything going on inside you, Capricorn. They will be particularly strong, and they will help you understand what is changing in you. Just be careful to distinguish your feelings from those of your (future?) partner.'),(334,'2022-12-28',10,'horoscope','If your best efforts to articulate your message are falling flat today, consider switching up your communication style. Under the glow of the empathic Pisces moon, fewer statements and more questions might do the trick.. If you’re not getting the positive feedback you’d like from other people, a minor adjustment to your tone or body language—or the way you phrase requests—might be in order. You don’t have to reinvent the wheel; just get aligned and rebalanced.'),(335,'2022-12-29',10,'horoscope','Your heart will feel full and optimistic this morning, dear Sea-Goat, as the moon enters Aries while forming a sweet alliance with auspicious Jupiter. Think positively and open yourself up to the idea that anything can happen while also tending to your needs and those of your loved ones. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus join forces in your sign, helping you find alignment between your thoughts and emotions. Take some time to tidy up your space later this evening when Luna blows a kiss to Mars. Check in with your feelings before the day comes to a close and the healing asteroid, Chiron, is active. '),(336,'2022-12-29',10,'horoscope','You\'re usually good at bringing people together. Your greatest strength is giving identity to those people who seek it. In fact, you\'re so aware of the differences between people that you resist the changes that come about as people evolve. Today\'s planetary alignment confronts you with issues that concern your future. Your position will help you accept things and go forward.'),(337,'2022-12-29',10,'horoscope','Try as you might to represent yourself authentically, there will always be people out there who simply don’t “get” you. But as Mercury turns retrograde in Capricorn and your self-expressed first house until January 18, you could trip yourself up letting these critics live rent-free in your head. Stop trying to win them over! Even if you do, it will be a hollow victory. Instead, shift your focus to places where there IS a natural click. Get involved (or re-involved!) in activities where you know you’ll rise and shine. The confidence boost will help you sail through these turbulent three weeks without too many bumps.'),(338,'2022-12-30',10,'horoscope','A nostalgic vibe will permeate the air today, dear Capricorn, inspiring you to embrace the music, food, fashion, and television shows that shaped you. Give yourself permission to delve deep into the past, but try to avoid painful memories, as this energy prefers optimism. Consider investing in your space when Luna blows a kiss to Saturn this evening, encouraging you to spoil yourself with a few fancy home goods. Watch out for drama and miscommunications later tonight when the moon forms a tense square with Mercury, which will heighten sensitivities and could lead to over-the-top displays of emotion.'),(339,'2022-12-30',10,'horoscope',' It takes two to tango, Capricorn. Remember that life isn\'t a one-way street. There needs to be a bit of give and take if you expect others to treat you the way you want to be treated. Don\'t let people take control when it comes to taking charge of your own life. Others may be emotional and stubborn. Don\'t waste your breath with useless drivel. Say something meaningful.'),(340,'2022-12-30',10,'horoscope','Chestnuts roasting on an open fire? Today\'s family-friendly moon calls for cozy bonding moments. Whip up a batch of hot toddies and invite your coterie of confidantes to your place for a pre-NYE potluck. Since you’ll be especially sentimental today, take time to honor your emotions as they arise. You\'re a human being, not a machine. And while you want to be productive, driving yourself like a taskmaster is no way to honor all the hard work you did this year. It’s time to log off, Capricorn, and trust that you’ll pick up the ball again in 2023!'),(341,'2022-12-31',10,'horoscope','The energy will feel grounding yet playful today, dear Capricorn, as the moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs fun. Though you\'re one of the most ambitious and success-oriented members of the zodiac, this luminary placement will ask that you put all of that aside for a moment, opting to focus on blowing off steam and connecting with your friends instead. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto collide in your sign, bringing a transformative energy to your image. These vibes present the perfect excuse for indulging in a makeover, so don\'t shy away from the urge to update your wardrobe or try a new hairstyle in anticipation of the new year.'),(342,'2022-12-31',10,'horoscope','A close friend may share some vital secret with you. You need to be very discreet with this information and offer appropriate sympathy and advice. Tackle all the tasks in your life in a constructive way. Your actions are especially powerful now and are likely to have a long term effect on those around you. So, you need to be careful about what you say or do'),(343,'2022-12-31',10,'horoscope','You get up from the bed today with a strong desire to prove your metal to the world. Enthusiastic and jovial, you are in your best possible mood.\n\nYou will seek approval of your family members for actions. The hard work you will do at work will surely get appreciated and rewarded by the end of the day.'),(344,'2022-12-21',11,'horoscope','Holiday season or not, it’s YOUR annual month to downshift and let life fall into an easier, more leisurely groove. That’s not your preferred speed, but today, as the ego-focused Sun shifts into Capricorn and your restful, relaxed twelfth house for four weeks, you may naturally slow your roll. This is a crucial time for you to unwind and recharge your personal energetic batteries: On January 19, el Sol will march into your sign and put you back in the driver’s seat—of a race car!'),(345,'2022-12-21',11,'horoscope','Boundaries will be a major theme for you in the coming weeks, dear Aquarius, as the sun enters Capricorn and the sector of your chart that governs privacy. This solar placement will coax you to go within so that you can sort through your deepest thoughts and feelings. However, embracing quiet and introspection will also require that you take space from your social sphere, but try not to ice out your family and friends without explanation. Luckily, you\'ll find yourself in a chatty mood this evening when the Sagittarius moon connects with the healing asteroid, Chiron. '),(346,'2022-12-21',11,'horoscope',' Be careful about the way your words come across to others, Aquarius. You might not realize how much other people\'s feelings are affected until it\'s too late. Consider backing off for a while and taking a break from your normal performance. Practice your lines at home. You may be in a bit of a funk, but the good news is that you will snap out of it very soon.'),(347,'2022-12-22',11,'horoscope','Come in for a landing! With dreamy Venus floating through your ethereal twelfth house and aligned with your ruler, restless Uranus, in your domestic zone, you may not have the attention span to concentrate on any one task for too long. And that’s perfectly okay! Shuffle your to-do list so you can work on more creative or social aspects of your job, saving the number-crunching for a more focused day. Any homey touches you can bring to work (flowers, a chill playlist, your slippers!) will help you really get into the mood.'),(348,'2022-12-22',11,'horoscope','The energy will be playful and sweet at home today, dear Aquarius, as Venus shares a helpful exchange with revolutionary Uranus. Lean into these supportive vibes by embracing love in all of its forms, nurturing both yourself and the people who matter most to you. This cosmic climate is also great for breaking up the routine within your domestic life, so be sure to treat your housemates to a surprise cocktail hour or exotic dinner. You\'ll notice a shift as the witching hour nears and the moon moves into Capricorn, putting you in a quiet and private headspace.  '),(349,'2022-12-22',11,'horoscope','The world probably isn\'t going to revolve around you today, Aquarius, so get used to it. Even though this may not be the news you want to hear, it\'s probably the news you most need to hear. Use your incredible passion to nurture others. Think less about yourself and more about the people around you, especially your family. Stick close to home and take care of chores.'),(350,'2022-12-23',11,'horoscope','Ready, set, downshift! Today\'s skies feature the year’s second Capricorn new moon, which also happens to be an empowering supermoon, in your twelfth house of introspection, relaxation and healing. It may not be an easy transition going from your hectic pace of life to slow and easy, but try! Start by doing a little digital detox, letting folks know they won’t be seeing you in the usual virtual places. Then pick a few books or creative projects to throw yourself into over the next two weeks. Download some guided meditations and listen to at least one a day. In the background, invite your muse to help you set some personal goals for the coming year. And then pursue them—gently! '),(351,'2022-12-23',11,'horoscope','It\'s okay if you don\'t feel like socializing today, dear Aquarius, as the Capricorn new moon activates the sector of your chart that governs privacy and secrets. This cosmic climate will encourage you to work from behind the scenes, hypothesizing on your next bold move from the comfort of seclusion. These vibes are also perfect for finding closure and breaking patterns, so don\'t be afraid to embrace movement. Excitement will fill your home later tonight when Luna shares a sweet exchange with Uranus, making it a good time to host a dance party for you and your housemates. '),(352,'2022-12-23',11,'horoscope','Ready, set, downshift! Today\'s skies feature the year’s second Capricorn new moon, which also happens to be an empowering supermoon, in your twelfth house of introspection, relaxation and healing. It may not be an easy transition going from your hectic pace of life to slow and easy, but try! Start by doing a little digital detox, letting folks know they won’t be seeing you in the usual virtual places. Then pick a few books or creative projects to throw yourself into over the next two weeks. Download some guided meditations and listen to at least one a day. In the background, invite your muse to help you set some personal goals for the coming year. And then pursue them—gently!'),(353,'2022-12-24',11,'horoscope','You greet the day energized! Your confidence is at an all-time high because of recent events. You have every reason to be proud of what you\'ve accomplished, especially at work. But your love life could benefit from the same level of commitment. Why not be proactive? Arrange a romantic evening for you and your partner. What a difference a few hours can make in your relationship!'),(354,'2022-12-24',11,'horoscope','You may receive messages of support from beyond the veil early this morning, dear Aquarius, as the Capricorn moon crosses over sweet Venus. Use this energy as an excuse to go deep within, showing yourself plenty of love and compassion. Good vibes will flow as Mercury blows a kiss to Neptune, encouraging you to appreciate your surroundings while taking a temporary break from the plights of our world. You\'ll have a chance to close doors this evening when Luna crosses over Pluto, bringing a transformative and cleaning energy to the table. The vibe will shift as the day comes to a close and the moon enters your sign, bringing a pep to your step. '),(355,'2022-12-24',11,'horoscope','Your energy levels improve and you don’t feel as if you are swimming against the tide. Advice from a mature person will make you feel more at ease about the recent dramatic events that have transpired in your life. Lucky Colour: Ash. Lucky Number: 2'),(356,'2022-12-25',11,'horoscope','The moon moves through your sign today, dear Aquarius, lifting your spirits and the energy that surrounds you. Don\'t be surprised if people gravitate toward you right now, placing you at the center of attention in group settings. Though your focus will be in high demand, remember to take breaks throughout the day in order to stay grounded and find your center. A creative streak will find you later in the afternoon thanks to a sweet exchange between Luna and Mars, marking the perfect moment to mix up your day. However, you should consider laying low later tonight when the moon squares Uranus.'),(357,'2022-12-25',11,'horoscope','The more you let your ego and fantasies swell today, Aquarius, the more friction you will encounter. Others aren\'t going to be fooled, nor are they going to want to deal with frivolity. You might consider letting someone else take the lead while you focus more on your internal energy. Don\'t be surprised if you cry for no apparent reason. It\'s important that the tears come out.'),(358,'2022-12-25',11,'horoscope','Some guests will arrive at your home. Students will also concentrate fully on their studies. There will be favorable conditions in business or job. You will make best use of opportunities that are presented to you. By God\'s grace your work will also get finished in time. Don\'t give importance to people who are jealous of you. You will have the support of your family. You will also explore new areas of business and plan a major expansion. You will meet new people and exchange your views with them. You will also meet some prominent personality. Your disputes relating to property will be resolved with the help of a mediator or mutual understanding. Both the parties stand to gain out of it.\n\n'),(359,'2022-12-26',11,'horoscope','Try not to lose your cool today, dear Aquarius, as the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. These vibes could cause you to put your foot in your mouth, especially when it comes to your professional life. Luckily, you\'ll have a chance to find your center and make wise moves as the moon moves through your sign, forming a celestial union with responsible Saturn. Work with this energy by accessing your authoritative side. Just remember to find your zen as well. You\'ll notice a shift later tonight when Luna enters Pisces, encouraging you to embrace a bit of luxury.'),(360,'2022-12-26',11,'horoscope',' Get your life in order today, Aquarius. Shed the false persona you\'ve been wearing and really look in the mirror. Make sure you like the person you see. This is a good day to put frivolity aside and concentrate on what you need to accomplish. Tend to your duties and plan wisely for the future. Store up your resources instead of squandering them all now.'),(361,'2022-12-26',11,'horoscope','Like it or not, all eyes will be on you today as the moon teams up with restrained—yet attention-commanding—Saturn in Aquarius. This is your moment to be the backbone of the group, but your humanitarian sign is more interested in promoting an unappreciated cause than tooting your own trumpet. Still, this mashup emphasizes YOUR needs—and you are only human. Let someone close to you know how much you appreciate them, but don’t be afraid to make a request if you need some support yourself!'),(362,'2022-12-27',11,'horoscope','Connecting with nature can help you find inner peace this morning, dear Aquarius, thanks to a supportive exchange between the sun and moon. At the very least, you should attempt to find beauty in your surroundings, which will have a grounding and gratitude-inducing effect on you. Try not to spend impulsively later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars, which could impair your financial judgment. The nodes of fate will push you to nurture yourself this evening, making it a great time to embrace domestic bliss.  Meanwhile, Venus and Neptune align in the skies, bringing tranquility to your psyche. '),(363,'2022-12-27',11,'horoscope','It may be upsetting to you, Aquarius, but there\'s something you need to think about. You should finally get it through your head that the people you often call \"brilliant\"\" are only reflections of you. If this month you decide to have a little faith in yourself and assert yourself a little'),(364,'2022-12-27',11,'horoscope','If you’re fixating on job stress or feeling anxious about money, it’s probably not ALL in your head. But there’s also no light at the end of that worry spiral. Nine times out of ten, you find an answer, Aquarius. And you’re far better equipped to do so when you’re grounded and centered. It won’t take much to get there. The hardest part is pulling yourself out of that fog so you can hop on the treadmill, dance to a few tracks on your playlist or do a ten-minute meditation. Don’t be surprised if a creative solution arises once you’ve turned your attention AWAY from the problem'),(365,'2022-12-28',11,'horoscope','You\'ll be in a unique position to spot beauty today, dear Aquarius, as the moon continues its journey through Pisces and your solar second house. These vibes are all about being present and observant, so be sure to appreciate your surroundings. Feel free to treat yourself to a bit of luxury when Luna cozies up to Neptune, but try not to go overboard with the spending. A sense of peace will surround you when the moon and Venus connect later in the afternoon, making the perfect occasion to meditate, journal, or seek solitude in the great outdoors.'),(366,'2022-12-28',11,'horoscope','It\'s possible that you\'re having some ups and downs in your love life at the moment. Someone may be asking you to play another role than you\'re used to playing in your relationship. Today, Aquarius, you should take the time to think about these pressures on you. You\'re going to need the answers to these questions over the next few months.'),(367,'2022-12-28',11,'horoscope','There’s nothing funny about money if it’s causing tension, Water Bearer. If you’ve been biting your tongue to keep the peace—while suffering in silence— today’s stars bring a chance to clear the air. The moon in your finance house catches a boost from diplomatic Venus, helping you articulate the issue instead of dropping hints. Whether someone owes you money and isn’t making overtures to compensate you or never pays their fair share, you’ll find your opening gambit. Just stay present in the conversation, and when you have a chance, bring it up without anger or resentment. '),(368,'2022-12-29',11,'horoscope','Your voice will carry a huge punch this morning, dear Aquarius, as the moon and Jupiter align in Aries and the sector of your chart that governs communication. Choose your words wisely and be sure to advocate for your agenda, and you\'ll soon manifest the outcome you\'ve been wishing for. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus align in the sky, asking you to show love and compassion to yourself. Consider working with positive mantras right now, especially if you\'ve had a hard time finding your optimism. A playful energy will come into play when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, encouraging you to seek excitement.'),(369,'2022-12-29',11,'horoscope','Some of you still let individuals from other Zodiac signs do all the creating for you. The planetary configuration today pushes you to free yourself from the ties that bind you. It\'s time for you to show more creativity. Show the gems that you usually hide. Express yourself fully, without hesitation. Show others who\'s really in charge.'),(370,'2022-12-29',11,'horoscope','No, Aquarius, it’s NOT selfish to prioritize your own need for solitude, fantasy or flow time. Today, Mercury flips into a three-week retrograde, drifting through the waters of your esoteric twelfth house. You may lose track of time and space as you explore your own psyche. Before you drift off, leave a few trail markers so the people who love you know that you’re coming back. For example, if you need some alone time, let your S.O. know, “you’ve done nothing wrong” or tell your best friends, “I’ll be back to hang out for NYE.” Deep healing is possible during this backspin, but make sure you don’t isolate too much!'),(371,'2022-12-30',11,'horoscope','Your mind may work faster than you can today, darling Aquarius, as the moon continues to move through fiery Aries and your solar third house. These vibes could have you bouncing from one task to the next, though it would be easy to leave projects unfinished if you don\'t take care to prioritize your tasks. Consider taking stock of your actions later this evening when Luna blows a kiss to Saturn, double-checking that you\'ve crossed each item from your to-do list. You may find yourself in a pensive mood later tonight as the moon squares off with Mercury, but try not to be snappy with your family and friends. '),(372,'2022-12-30',11,'horoscope',' It may be hard to resolve anything today, Aquarius. It could be that there\'s an overwhelming resistance making it difficult to act according to plan. Today isn\'t a good day to fight. If things don\'t seem to be going your way, don\'t push it. Trying to strong-arm the situation will only aggravate things and make them worse. You may need to make some compromises in order to maintain the peace.'),(373,'2022-12-30',11,'horoscope','Many hands make light work, so don\'t be a martyr when it comes to wrapping up those very final end-of-year tasks. It\'s not fair that you\'re racing around like a headless chicken while the benefactors of your hard work are barely lifting a finger. If you’re meant to be working as a team, take command and give everyone a task so you can enjoy some breathing room, too. Besides, collaborating makes the process a whole lot more entertaining. The only glitch? You\'ll have to let go of having everything done according to the Book of Aquarius'),(374,'2022-12-31',11,'horoscope','The moon migrates into Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs domestic bliss today, darling Water-Bearer, creating the ideal ambiance for a lazy weekend at home. Use this energy to get caught up on your favorite TV shows and podcasts, all from the comfort of your couch and coziest blankets. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto shake hands in the sector of your chart that governs the subconscious, asking you to face your shadow with love and compassion. These vibes will support you through any emotional or mental deep diving you\'re called to do, so don\'t be afraid to sit in your feelings before celebrating the new year.'),(375,'2022-12-31',11,'horoscope','The day may turn out to be somewhat bizarre. Event which you never expected have a high chance of happening today. It is important that you take note of the planetary energies and try to understand the direction to which they are pushing you. Detecting the right path at this juncture can have a revolutionary effect on your life'),(376,'2022-12-31',11,'horoscope','You will get success on the platter today. Enjoy the sweet taste of success.\n\nPeople around you will be pleasantly surprised to see a different side of your personality. Continue to be like this and have a good time while luck favours you, as every day is not the same say'),(377,'2022-12-21',12,'horoscope','Popularity: soaring! Today, the confident Sun kicks off a four-week regatta through Capricorn and your eleventh house of friends, parties and strategic socializing. Your charisma is running at record levels, and people will clamor to get close to you—so make the most of it! Whether for business or pleasure, you can deepen some important ties during this cycle. If you’ve got a product or message to promote, this is your moment. Let the bonding begin!'),(378,'2022-12-21',12,'horoscope','You\'ll be the glue that holds your social group together, dear Pisces, as the sun enters Capricorn and the sector of your chart that governs community. Whether you find yourself organizing gatherings, smoothing out conflict, or helping others make connections, the stars will ask you to bring people together. The vibe could get a bit emotionally charged this evening when the Sagittarius moon faces off with Mars, threatening to trigger mood swings within yourself and others. Luckily, you\'ll have a chance to ground in the present by indulging your senses, thanks to a helping hand from the healing asteroid, Chiron.  '),(379,'2022-12-21',12,'horoscope',' Today could be the day you\'ve been waiting for, Pisces. Realize that you have the gentle, sincere nature necessary to sweet-talk your way through any situation. Indeed, if there is something that needs resolution, now would be a good time to smooth things over. People will be more receptive to your good nature and nurturing qualities.'),(380,'2022-12-22',12,'horoscope','Don’t rush to any decisions today, Pisces. Part of you is highly focused on the practical aspects of a project (thanks to creative Venus in laser-like Capricorn), but a mashup with chaos agent Uranus in Taurus could confound your thought process. It’s a day to toggle between your logical left brain and your creative right, but then let your HEART make the final call. Ironically, you’ll be clear as a bell when it comes to helping others sort out conflicting situations!'),(381,'2022-12-22',12,'horoscope','You\'ll find yourself in a social mood today, dear Pisces, as Venus shares a sweet exchange with Uranus. These vibes are perfect for discussing unusual topics and breaking free from the ordinary, as doing so will strengthen your bonds while bringing fulfillment to your heart. Just remember to stay focused on your responsibilities for the day, as the Sagittarius moon blows a kiss to serious Saturn. Try not to take it personally if a loved one seems guarded this afternoon, as it likely has nothing to do with you. The vibe will shift later tonight when the moon enters Sagittarius, triggering the genius that lives within. '),(382,'2022-12-22',12,'horoscope',' Initiate a deep, meaningful conversation with someone you\'ve lost touch with, Pisces. It could be that a long and ugly point of contention is on the brink of resolution. All you need to do is make the first move. There\'s a great deal of heartfelt, loving energy in the air that will help you foster a sensitive, tender approach. Find a connection with someone that you didn\'t know was there.'),(383,'2022-12-23',12,'horoscope','When’s the last time you took the emotional pulse of Team Pisces? If you—or anyone on the squad—are less than delighted with each other and your collective success, you’ll have a golden opportunity to make some needed adjustments starting today. The year\'s second Capricorn new moon—also a potent supermoon—turns on the lights in your eleventh house of collaboration and technology. What have you been ignoring lately; how could things improve in these areas? You may have to have an uncomfortable conversation with someone, but if that helps the whole crew get back in high gear, it’ll be worth enduring an awkward hour or two. '),(384,'2022-12-23',12,'horoscope','The alliances you form today are likely to survive the test of time, dear Pisces, as the Capricorn moon activates your solar eleventh house. Use this energy to expand upon your network, taking care to reach out to anyone you hope to build a dynamic with. Opportunities for professional growth could also come into play, making it a good time to cash in on any favors you\'re owed. Surprising gossip may find you later tonight when Luna shares a sweet exchange with Uranus. However, try not to get caught up in conversations that could be misconstrued as negative or malicious. '),(385,'2022-12-23',12,'horoscope','When’s the last time you took the emotional pulse of Team Pisces? If you—or anyone on the squad—are less than delighted with each other and your collective success, you’ll have a golden opportunity to make some needed adjustments starting today. The year\'s second Capricorn new moon—also a potent supermoon—turns on the lights in your eleventh house of collaboration and technology. What have you been ignoring lately; how could things improve in these areas? You may have to have an uncomfortable conversation with someone, but if that helps the whole crew get back in high gear, it’ll be worth enduring an awkward hour or two. '),(386,'2022-12-24',12,'horoscope','You have strong humanitarian instincts, Pisces. You think of your fellow humans more than most. This, combined with your intuition and empathy, makes you well suited for the healing professions. If you\'ve felt a bit disgruntled at work lately, it may be that you\'re in the wrong career. Consider training as a counselor or therapist. You would be good at it and help a lot of people.'),(387,'2022-12-24',12,'horoscope','You\'ll feel like the center of attention when you awaken this morning, dear Pisces, as the Capricorn moon crosses over sweet Venus. People will look to you for guidance under this cosmic climate. However, try not to feel obligated to solve issues that don\'t belong to you. Meanwhile, Mercury blows a kiss to ethereal Neptune, blessing your voice with grace and the ability to reach many. Don\'t be afraid to stand on your platform when Luna crosses over Pluto, encouraging you to step into your power. You\'ll find yourself in a more private mood as the day comes to a close and the moon enters Aquarius.'),(388,'2022-12-24',12,'horoscope',' Your dreamy disposition attracts admirers, but are you ready to act on it? Too much deliberation is not a good thing. Don\\\'t take your frustrations out on the ones you love. You experience delays or additional red tape in official work. Today you work, but also enjoy a sense of accomplishment. Lucky Colour: Ivory. Lucky Number: 5.'),(389,'2022-12-25',12,'horoscope','You may feel like more of a spectator than participant today, dear Pisces, as the moon moves through Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs privacy. Though the holiday may bring forth plenty of activity, don\'t feel guilty about assuming the role of wallflower. Luckily, you\'ll feel more animated later in the afternoon when Luna blows a kiss to Mars, helping you find comfort amongst your most nurturing companionships. You may need to excuse yourself from stimulating environments as the day comes to a close and Luna squares off with Uranus, thrusting you into a solitary headspace.'),(390,'2022-12-25',12,'horoscope','The hard work and detail-oriented planning you\'ve done lately are really starting to pay off, Pisces. The key is to maintain your sensitivity and look to where you can be of service to others. Your nurturing side feels the need to express itself. Follow your heart today and be respectful of your emotions. The thing you need to be most conscious of is not overextending yourself.'),(391,'2022-12-25',12,'horoscope','Some guests will arrive at your home. Students will also concentrate fully on their studies. There will be favorable conditions in business or job. You will make best use of opportunities that are presented to you. By God\'s grace your work will also get finished in time. Don\'t give importance to people who are jealous of you. You will have the support of your family. You will also explore new areas of business and plan a major expansion. You will meet new people and exchange your views with them. You will also meet some prominent personality. Your disputes relating to property will be resolved with the help of a mediator or mutual understanding. Both the parties stand to gain out of it.\n\n'),(392,'2022-12-26',12,'horoscope','You can\'t buy your way toward personal evolution, dear Pisces, a fact the universe will attempt to remind you of when the South Node forms an unbalanced aspect with Chiron. While investing in new tools, clothes, or accessories may help you feel like you\'re heading in a new direction, true change comes from within. Luckily, you\'ll have a chance to honestly examine your life when the Aquarius moon cozies up to Saturn, helping you close doors and move away from situations or behaviors holding you back. You\'ll feel more optimistic as the day comes to a close and the moon makes its debut in your sign.'),(393,'2022-12-26',12,'horoscope','You will fit in perfectly with just about every situation you encounter today, Pisces. Things are going well for you, so take advantage of the energy. You will find that you can accomplish a lot with very little effort. Other people will respect that. If something needs to be done meticulously and efficiently, you\'re the one for the job'),(394,'2022-12-26',12,'horoscope','Flex the muscles of your helping hands. You may be in particularly charitable spirits today as the moon links up with grounded Saturn in your twelfth house of healing. Your urge to give time, money or advice to a loved one in need is admirable, but don’t cross the line between compassion and fostering codependence. And remember, ‘ giving one: Generosity is a two-way street. When you let someone help you, you’re giving THEM the gift of good karma!'),(395,'2022-12-27',12,'horoscope','Your community will acknowledge you as a rising star this morning, dear Fish, as the moon travels through your sign and blows a kiss to the sun. Use this energy to step into your extroverted side, nurturing your image through pleasantries and social exchange. Unfortunately, the vibe will get a little rough later in the afternoon when Luna squares off with Mars. These vibes are poised to heighten your emotions, marking a good time to unplug and hide away at home. Meanwhile, Venus shares a sweet exchange with Neptune, allowing you to feel the love from your friends far and wide. '),(396,'2022-12-27',12,'horoscope','What a great day for you! You seem to have the innate listening abilities of a therapist or counselor. Everyone comes to you with their problems or to cry on your proverbial shoulder. They know that you will listen without judgment. Have you ever thought about doing something like this for a living? Perhaps today will make you think about it.'),(397,'2022-12-27',12,'horoscope','Why yes, they ARE checking you out, Pisces. The moon beams in your sign today, turning up the dial on your charisma. Even if you’re feeling a tad self-conscious, don\'t pull a classic Pisces disappearing act. Single Fish can reel in an adoring new admirer simply by paying them your full attention. (You can be positively hypnotic when you choose to turn on the charm.) Don’t underestimate how much you add to your existing social circles. There’s nothing to prepare. Just show up and be fully engaged with whatever’s going on!'),(398,'2022-12-28',12,'horoscope','You\'ll feel energized, creative, and beloved today, dear Pisces, as the moon continues to travel through your sign. Use this energy to nurture your goals and personal agendas, as the universe will be eager to open up pathways. Pay attention to your creative thoughts when Luna cozies up to Neptune this afternoon, helping you align with your spirituality and artistic self. A new admirer may reveal themselves later in the day, thanks to a sweet exchange between the moon and Venus. Consider purging your social media feeds of any triggering accounts later tonight when Pluto is active in our skies.'),(399,'2022-12-28',12,'horoscope',' Today you may get the opportunity to feel proud of yourself. But don\'t let things get too out of hand. It isn\'t often that you allow yourself this little bit of narcissism. Everything you say will be pertinent, and people will let you know. For once, the stars are giving you the opportunity to cater to your own ego, so take advantage of it!'),(400,'2022-12-28',12,'horoscope','A little burst of momentum comes your way today, courtesy of the Pisces moon. If you’ve been waffling about next steps, this may provide the necessary nudge to at least take the first action step toward a daunting goal. Of course you WANT to make a change, Pisces, but there are underlying reasons you haven’t. Sometimes we need someone to lead the way or to lean on until we get traction. This might be a therapist, coach or support group. Acknowledging you need a little help is actually a sign of tremendous strength, not to mention wisdom.'),(401,'2022-12-29',12,'horoscope','A prosperous energy will find you today, darling Pisces, as the Aries moon and lucky Jupiter align in the sector of your chart that governs money. Work with these vibes by boldly pursuing monetary success, and be sure to work with positive mantras, while carrying your favorite money-drawing stones. Meanwhile, Mercury and Venus hold hands in Capricorn, asking you to lift up your community with positive words and compassion. Plan on embracing luxury from the comfort of home later in the afternoon, when Luna blows a kiss to fiery Mars. Take a moment to ground in the present before the day comes to a close when Luna and Chiron align.'),(402,'2022-12-29',12,'horoscope','You are very interested in all kinds of professions that concern humans, Pisces - medicine, psychology, or any kind of spiritual therapy. You will be very sensitive to the great opening toward the future that comes along today. The planetary alignment initiates progress in all areas of human existence. Keep your eyes and ears wide open'),(403,'2022-12-29',12,'horoscope','NYE reunion, anyone? Social Mercury flips into retrograde today, backing up through your communal eleventh house until January 18. While that might not sound like toast-worthy news, there’s a hidden opportunity tucked in this nostalgic three-week cycle. Friends from your past could come out of the woodwork—perhaps you’ll add them as latecomers to your weekend guest list? In early 2023, there’s no need to reinvent any wheels for your winter fun. Circle back with organizations and extracurriculars that you enjoyed being a part of in the past. They’ll greet you with open arms'),(404,'2022-12-30',12,'horoscope','Remember to pace yourself today, dear Pisces, as the moon continues its journey through fiery Aries and your solar second house. Though you\'ll feel eager to handle your business and finish tasks, moving hastily could cause you to disconnect from the present moment. Take a few moments for solitude as Luna blows a kiss to Saturn, encouraging quiet and introspection. You should be mindful of who you surround yourself with later tonight, as a harsh square between the moon and Mercury could lead to major miscommunications and drama. These vibes also suggest it may be a good evening to unplug, lest you find yourself in an online feud.'),(405,'2022-12-30',12,'horoscope',' Intense emotions are apt to dominate the scene today, Pisces. Don\'t do anything halfway. It\'s time to give it your all or nothing. You have the power to cut to the heart of the issue. Don\'t hesitate. If you meet opposition, stay strong. There\'s a valuable lesson to be learned. If you\'re being true to yourself, you should have no trouble overcoming any obstacle that stands in your path.'),(406,'2022-12-30',12,'horoscope','Admit it, Pisces: You prefer starting projects to finishing them, and with your meandering mind, you\'re easily distracted. Yet those loose ends can weigh on you, obstructing mental space. Take inventory today as the year is officially almost over. Which of these seeds of genius are worth cultivating in 2023 and which would be better off put on indefinite hold? It wouldn’t hurt to pack away supplies that you won’t be using for a while. Think of it as a New Year’s decluttering for your space AND your psyche!'),(407,'2022-12-31',12,'horoscope','You\'ll be in a cool, collected, and social mood today, dear Pisces, as the moon enters grounded Taurus and the sector of your chart that governs communication. Whether your new year plans involve a big night out or staying in, these vibes will encourage you to check in with your family and friends. Your words will also carry a certain weight, making it a good time to journal your resolutions for 2023. Meanwhile, Venus and Pluto shake hands in your solar eleventh house, bringing the promise of new connections throughout the next twelve months, so you may want to prepare yourself for plenty of networking.'),(408,'2022-12-31',12,'horoscope','You are blessed with an amazingly clear vision today and you will be able to weigh long term benefits of your actions correctly. Hence, today is a good time to judge new ventures and investments which have come your way so that you can arrive at an objective decision. You will also be able to judge the persons near to you and identify who is your genuine well wisher.'),(409,'2022-12-31',12,'horoscope','Today being a slightly risky day for, tread cautiously when it comes to financial dealings. Read the fine print and thoroughly thrash out the nitty-gritty of any contracts you commit to.\n\nAny mistakes made now could come back later and extract a heavy price. There are also chances of conflict with your partner or spouse');
