INSERT INTO `yearly_horoscope` VALUES (1,'2022-01-01',8,'horoscope','As this holiday month gets underway, Capricorn, you’re in a phase of completion in which it would be wise to tie up loose ends. The coming weeks until December 21 are your opportunity to find closure on issues that have been holding you back or sapping your energy. They might rise to the surface at this time, so you’ll have no choice but to deal with them. And if you need help handling anything, ask for it.'),(2,'2023-01-01',8,'horoscope','The emphasis is on your sign, Capricorn, with the sun here until January 20 encouraging you to express yourself and share your talents with the world. It’s an opportunity to focus on yourself for a change and get involved in activities that are close to your heart.However, with chatty Mercury retrograde in this sector until the eighteenth, you’ll still need to take care with deals and negotiations and be aware that delays are possible. Still, this shouldn’t stop you from focusing on your future and setting goals that really resonate with you.'),(3,'2024-01-01',8,'horoscope','You\'ll feel empowered to embrace change today, dear Capricorn, as the Taurus moon aspects transformative Pluto. These vibes are perfect for saying \"goodbye\" to drama and \"hello\" to your fabulous future! Your creativity will also benefit from a cosmic boost, making it a good time to work on any passion projects you\'ve been nurturing. You\'ll feel a shift as Venus enters Aquarius this evening, bringing forth an era of prosperity, luxury, and a sense of gratitude. You\'ll feel inclined to get organized and strategize for your goals once Luna enters Gemini, forming supportive connections with sweet Venus and lucky Jupiter. ');
